Description: He always wears an iron mask, and rumor has it that he's actually very handsome.
DescriptionJP: いつも鉄の仮面をつけている。 その素顔はハンサムという噂も…。

Name: Joe Divide
Description: This agreeable chap loves nature. He can also converse with his late ancestors.
DescriptionJP: 自然を愛するナイスガイ。 精霊たちと会話できるらしい。

Name: Sam Willing
Description: He believes that if he scrunches his eyes shut, he'll become invisible.
DescriptionJP: 意識を集中させるために目を閉じている。 なぜ その必要があるのかは誰も知らない。

Name: Mary Antoine
Description: A sophisticated girl with refined tastes. She prefers cake to bread.
DescriptionJP: 気品あふれる姿が美しい。 パンよりケーキが好き？

Name: Edward Baron
Description: He claims to be royalty. You never know, he might be telling the truth...
DescriptionJP: 王様だと言い張っている。 本当にどこかの王族かも…。

Name: Tim Platton
Description: An amateur treasure hunter who likes diving for sunken treasure.
DescriptionJP: 財宝探しが趣味。 今日もどこかの海に潜っている。

Name: Argento Salvage
Description: His hobby is searching for sunken treasure with his friends.
DescriptionJP: 財宝探しが趣味。 仲間とともに探している。

Name: Finn Geld
Description: An amateur treasure hunter who may have just struck gold.
DescriptionJP: 財宝探しが趣味。 ついに埋蔵金を発見したらしい。

Name: Ian Moray
Description: An elusive lad who just can't stay still for one minute.
DescriptionJP: つかみどころが無い ひょうひょうとした夏男。

Name: Gil Holden
Description: A swimming pro who can stay underwater for ages.
DescriptionJP: 水泳がとっても得意！ 長時間でも潜っていられる。

Name: Doyle Palmer
Description: He loves the tropics and has a passion for passion fruits.
DescriptionJP: 南国が大好き。 特にパッションフルーツが大好物。

Name: Audry Orange
Description: Even in the depths of winter, she's bright and full of life.
DescriptionJP: 冬の寒さもなんのその いつでも元気なミカン娘。

Name: May Apple
Description: She tries to act mature, but she's still green around the edges.
DescriptionJP: 本人は大人ぶってるが まだまだ青い。

Name: Ginny White
Description: She likes to sleep during the day so she can avoid getting sunburned.
DescriptionJP: 日焼けを極端にキラい 昼間は寝ている色白娘。

Name: Angus Hogg
Description: He grew up in the great outdoors and has a deep rustic suntan.
DescriptionJP: のびのびと大自然で育ったので かなり日焼けしている。

Name: Sabrina Carow
Description: She unsettles her friends by always reciting incantations.
DescriptionJP: いつも呪文を唱えているので 友達は気味悪がっている。

Name: Bob Beelzy
Description: His harsh exterior hides his true tender-hearted nature.
DescriptionJP: 見かけとは裏腹に 優しい心の持ち主。

Name: Patt Howell
Description: This rowdy ruffian races round shouting and bothering his neighbors.
DescriptionJP: 大声を出して走り回るので 近所では迷惑がられている。

Name: Ol Factory
Description: He can distinguish things by smell. Which won't help him a great deal on the pitch.
DescriptionJP: あらゆるものを嗅ぎ分ける。 活かせるスポーツが無いのが悩み。

Name: Tom Skipper
Description: He wants nothing more than to sail the high seas as a pirate king.
DescriptionJP: 世界中の海を股にかける大海賊に憧れて 今日も 荒れ狂う海原を突き進む夢を見る。

Name: Colin Binder
Description: A collector of cool things. He has to catalogue them all in a file.
DescriptionJP: 綺麗なものに目がないコレクター。 何事もファイルしないと気が済まない。

Name: Larry Pogue
Description: A cheerful, popular guy despite the pittance he gets for pocket money.
DescriptionJP: 存在が光るみんなの人気者。 月のお小遣いが１５８円。

Name: Rob Cardson
Description: He loves card games and likes to play snap with red and yellow cards.
DescriptionJP: カードゲームの達人。 イエローカードさえも切り札に。

Name: Ken Mayfield
Description: When it comes to a certain football video game, he's the world's greatest.
DescriptionJP: とあるサッカーゲームの最強プレイヤー。 どんなときでも キミの挑戦を待っている。

Name: Casey Leather
Description: A highly-skilled player, his black-and-white hair makes him look like a football.
DescriptionJP: 髪は白黒でまるでサッカーボール。 誰にもマネできないテクニックで勝負。

Name: Ethan Swallow
Description: He boasts of being as fast as Nathan Swift, and can move his hair at will.
DescriptionJP: 髪の毛を自由にあやつれる？ 自慢は風丸にも負けないスピード！

Name: Bob Daruma
Description: He gets right back up no matter how many times he is knocked over.
DescriptionJP: 何度こけてもすぐ起き上がる ど根性の持ち主。

Name: Mitch Blackston
Description: A mysterious shadowy figure who shoots with bruised and battered legs.
DescriptionJP: キズだらけの足でシュートを放つ！ 闇から来たという 謎の少年。

Name: In Chikita
Description: The nation's number one choreographer rocks a trademark afro hairstyle.
DescriptionJP: 振り付けをさせたら日本一！！ でっかいアフロが目印。

Name: Austin Hobbes
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He idolizes Axel Blaze, yet has some incredible latent abilities of his own...
DescriptionJP: 豪炎寺に憧れる少年。 潜在能力は未知数。

Name: Archer Hawkins
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Rumors are rife about this shady character. They call him Kid Kickalot.
DescriptionJP: ナゾの多い少年。 『蹴りのトビー』の異名を持つ。

Name: Xavier Foster
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: There was a time when he went by "Xene" and led Alius Academy. His shots rip through the air like comets.
DescriptionJP: かつてグランを名乗りエイリア学園を率いた。 そのシュートは まるで彗星のごとし。

Name: Jordan Greenway
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Though known for his cold nature among his peers from Alius Academy, beneath the facade actually lies an affectionate personality.
DescriptionJP: エイリア学園では冷酷さを売りにしていたが 実は演じていただけらしく 人懐っこい性格。

Name: Caleb Stonewall
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His boastful bragging stands out, but he does have the skill to back it up. He makes playthings of others with his trick plays.
DescriptionJP: 傲慢な言動が目立つが その実力は本物。 トリックプレイで周りを翻弄する。

Name: Percival Travis
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The manager representing Japan, at Hillman's recommendation. He competes calmly, using perfectly calculated strategies.
DescriptionJP: 響木が推薦した 日本代表監督。 完璧に計算された作戦で 冷静に立ち向かう。

Name: Camellia Travis
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An old friend of Mark's. Quite bashful, but she's grown thanks to training.
DescriptionJP: 円堂守の幼馴染みで ちょっと内気な少女。 イナズマジャパンのマネージャーを務める。

Name: Isaac Glass
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Unlike his brother, he's actually good at football. But he's nowhere near as brainy...
DescriptionJP: 兄の欠流とは違い 天才的なプレイヤー。 しかし 恐ろしいほどにメンタルが弱い。

Name: Gene Whalon
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Australia's star keeper, who uses the power of water to block the shots that come his way.
DescriptionJP: オージー最強のキーパー。 彼こそ真のポセイドン。

Name: David Waterman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He cut his teeth on Aussie Rules football, but joined the Big Waves to take on the world.
NameJP: デビット・ウォーターマン
DescriptionJP: もともとはオージーフットボールの選手だが 大会に憧れて参加。

Name: Sonny Shore
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An eco-warrior who can't bear the sight of a polluted beach.
DescriptionJP: 砂浜が汚れているのが我慢できなくて 毎日ごみ拾いをしている。

Name: Kjell Snapper
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player applies the wisdom of the ancients to his style of play.
DescriptionJP: オーストラリアに太古から伝わる アートの伝承者。

Name: Ken Crackham
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: As well as a footballer, this player is an active conservationist of Australia's rich biodiversity.
DescriptionJP: オーストラリアにしかいない 珍しい生き物の保護に熱心。

Name: Shawn Princeton
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player has a prodigious knack for finding rare minerals just by reading the landscape.
NameJP: シュリー・プリンストン
DescriptionJP: 珍しい鉱物のありかを見つける天才。 地形を見ただけで分かるらしい。

Name: Matt Fischer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Patience strengthened by spiritual discipline is the key to this player's power.
DescriptionJP: チャンスをうかがうために じっと耐えることのできる精神力の持ち主。

Name: Hank Tennyson
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This international soul-surfer spends his life in pursuit of the ultimate wave.
DescriptionJP: サーフィンの世界的な名手。 いつも海をながめて いい波を待っている。

Name: Dolph Hensen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A noble son of the majestic sea, and the captain of the Australian squad.
DescriptionJP: 華麗なる海の貴公子と呼ばれるＭＦ。 オーストラリア代表チームを率いる。

Name: Hamilton Reith
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player's hobby is free diving for tropical fish amid the coral reefs.
DescriptionJP: サンゴ礁で素潜りをして 熱帯魚を捕まえる名人。

Name: Joe Dawes
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A stealthy player who creeps up to rivals slowly, then pounces suddenly.
DescriptionJP: 静かに相手に忍び寄り チャンスとなると一気に襲いかかる。

Name: Quincy Horace
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: As a sideline, this player tries to locate new goldmines in the outback.
NameJP: クインシー・ホースト
DescriptionJP: 今でも 新たな金鉱を探して 荒野を旅している。

Name: Holly Summers
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He dresses up as Santa every year, but it's pretty sweaty work where he lives.
DescriptionJP: 毎年サンタのバイトをしているが 暑くて 寒い地域がうらやましい。

Name: Derek Rabson
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A very skillful player who can cut deep into his rivals' midfield.
DescriptionJP: 鋭い腕の使い方で 相手の中に切り込んでいくのがうまい。

Name: Barack Daniels
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A jackaroo who dreams of producing the world's tastiest beef someday.
DescriptionJP: 家で飼っているオーストラリア牛の肉を 世界一にしようとがんばっている。

Name: Bruce Marlin
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Rivals had better be careful of this player's kangaroo-style footwork.
DescriptionJP: カンガルーのように バネのあるフットワークで切り込んでいく。

Name: Robert Kleiser
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Manager of Big Waves. Adapts his strategy like a flowing, unpredictable tide.
NameJP: ロベルト・クライザー
DescriptionJP: ビッグウェイブスの監督。 状況に応じた 多彩な戦術を展開する。

Name: Nasir Mustafa
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A scion of a powerful tribe, he cannot return home unless it is to announce victory.
DescriptionJP: 有力部族の息子。「大会に勝てるまで 帰ってくるな」と言われている。

Name: Faraz Farooq
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player's famous for making delicious desserts with dates.
DescriptionJP: ナツメヤシの実を加工して いろんなお菓子を作るのがうまい。

Name: Bilal Kalil
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A shadowy man who leads his team with a relentless energy.
DescriptionJP: デザートライオンのキャプテンを務める。 どこか陰のある雰囲気のディフェンダー。

Name: Jamila Wali
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A keen traveler, this player dreams of a world which is not dependent on fossil fuels.
NameJP: ジャメル・ジャマドゥ
DescriptionJP: 観光に力を入れて 石油に頼らない国を目指そうとしている。

Name: Musa Sylla
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player wants to improve Qatar's manufacturing base and diversify.
DescriptionJP: 石油を輸出するだけでなく カタールの工業に活かせないか考えている。

Name: Yusuf Massoud
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player deeply respects tribal traditions, and wouldn't like to live away from home.
DescriptionJP: 伝統を重んじる部族の１人で 外国の文化に馴染めない。

Name: Sulayk Sulaiman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player hopes to help Qatar by finding a cheap way to desalinate seawater.
NameJP: スライ・スライマーン
DescriptionJP: カタールのみんなのために 安く海水を真水にする方法を考えている。

Name: Sayid Armand
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player is concerned that his country's economy is dependent on oil exports.
DescriptionJP: 国の豊かさが 石油やガスに 頼りすぎていることを 心配している。

Name: Mansur Jasim
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player is an expert at finding natural pearls. They're pretty pricey these days.
DescriptionJP: 今では貴重になった 天然の真珠を見つける名人。

Name: Zack Abdulla
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Camel herding was the traditional occupation of this player's tribe.
DescriptionJP: ラクダの世話をさせたら部族一。 彼の言うことなら 何でも聞くらしい。

Name: Majdi Ismail
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: As a hobby, this player likes to collect reptiles in the desert and frighten little girls with them.
NameJP: マジディ・イスマイール
DescriptionJP: 砂漠のオオトカゲを捕まえる名人。 でも 苦手な人には見せないほうが。

Name: Talal Hamad
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The ultimate goal of this player is to be a newsreader on a Middle Eastern TV station.
DescriptionJP: 中東一のＴＶ局に入って 世界にニュースを送るのが夢。

Name: Hasan Ahmed
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This forward is known as the Eagle of Qatar for his swooping attacks.
DescriptionJP: カタールの鷹と呼ばれるほどの トップフォワード。

Name: Khalfan Jibril
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player is keen on preserving ancient mosques, and the fine arts of the Middle East.
NameJP: ハルファン・ジブリール
DescriptionJP: イスラムの優れた美術品を 守りたいと思っている。

Name: Rajab Ismail
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: With the dream of getting published, this player is working on a novel set in Qatar.
NameJP: ラジャブ・イスマイール
DescriptionJP: カタールの社会問題を小説にして みんなに訴えようとしている。

Name: Adel Siddique
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A budding filmmaker, this player hopes that one day he can produce real Qatari cinema.
DescriptionJP: カタールのみんなに愛される 大衆映画を作ろうとしている。

Name: Eliza Mannan
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Manager of the Desert Lions. Specializes in tactical second-half surges.
DescriptionJP: デザートライオンの監督。 試合後半に畳みかける戦術が得意。

Name: Zack Cummings
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Blocks the goalmouth with the huge frame he bulked up through martial arts.
DescriptionJP: 格闘技で鍛え上げた体で ゴールの前に立ちふさがる。

Name: Wilbur Watkins
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A dangerous player who pretends to shoot, only to scatter the opponent with the ball.
DescriptionJP: シュートに見せかけて 相手をボールで吹き飛ばす 危険なヤツ。

Name: Dave Quagmire
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Raimon first met this Gungnir-toting football fanatic in Kyoto back in his Dvalin days.
DescriptionJP: 相手が強敵であるほど気持ちが高ぶる。 サッカーへの熱い想いが止まらない。

Name: Zeke Valanche
Description: Has total confidence in his own skill, and blames those around him when things go wrong.
DescriptionJP: 自分の力に絶対の自信を持ち うまくいかないと周りのせいにする。

Name: Ethan Whitering
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Torch's childhood friend. He used to be a weakling, but training toughened him up.
DescriptionJP: バーンとは幼馴染み。 昔は病弱だったが 特訓で克服したという。

Name: Jeongsu Cho
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An ambitious player who wants to see Korean footballers on the world stage.
DescriptionJP: 韓国のサッカーのレベルアップのため 世界で活躍したいと思っている。

Name: Umi Hwang
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The heir to an industrial fortune, this player had the benefit of an elite education.
DescriptionJP: 大財閥の跡取りとして ずっとエリートとしての教育を受けてきた。

Name: Dooyoon Hong
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He can't handle spicy food, so he struggles with his home country's chili-laden cuisine.
DescriptionJP: 実は辛いものが苦手で いつも食事に苦労している。

Name: Minho Cho
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The fierce power of tae kwon do kicks are put to good use on the pitch by this player.
DescriptionJP: テコンドーの名手。 その猛烈なキック力を活かして サッカーに。

Name: Songhwan Ko
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Highly skilled in baseball and football, this player cannot decide which to go pro in.
DescriptionJP: サッカーも好きだが 野球も好き。 どっちでプロを目指すか 悩んでいる。

Name: Paekyeong Park
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Academics aren't this player's strong point, so he's hoping for a football scholarship.
DescriptionJP: 受験勉強するのが嫌で サッカーのうまさで 進学しようとしている。

Name: Eunyeong Kim
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This computer prodigy's only in middle school, but has already won medals as a pro gamer.
DescriptionJP: 中学生にして プロのネットゲーマー。 大会でのメダルは 数えられないほど。

Name: Claude Beacons
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A hot-blooded, aggressive striker. His scorching shots leave a trail of ash in their red-hot wake.
DescriptionJP: 血の気が多く攻撃的なストライカー。 灼熱のシュートは 全てを焦がして突き進む。

Name: Changsu Choi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A natural-born playmaker whose sharp control may even rival Jude.
DescriptionJP: ゲームメーカーとして天賦の才を発揮する。 その実力は 鬼道に勝るとも劣らない。

Name: Bryce Whitingale
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A quiet and cool-headed player. His plays leave the opposition frozen in their boots.
DescriptionJP: 静かさと冷徹さを持つ選手。 そのプレイは敵を凍てつかせる。

Name: Chi-Won Ho
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Being from southern Korea, he's not too keen on the cold winters in Seoul.
DescriptionJP: 南部の出身で 寒さに弱く ソウル暮らしはかなり厳しそう。

Name: Dong-Hyun Seul
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This aspiring filmmaker hopes to be recognized with an award someday.
DescriptionJP: 自分の作った映画で 世界一の賞を狙っている。

Name: Jung-Hoon Yi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player is well thought of for his good manners towards his elders.
DescriptionJP: 年長者を常に敬っているので 大人から いつも感心されている。

Name: Sung-Jin Noh
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player dreams of taking K-pop to the world stage. Well, the way things are going...
DescriptionJP: これから韓流スターとして 世界にはばたく予定。あくまでも予定。

Name: Joon-Ho Ja
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Applying technical ingenuity, this player hopes to open markets for new digital devices.
DescriptionJP: 自分の考えた家電が 世界中で販売されるのが夢。

Name: Lee Ji Seong
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Manager of Fire Dragon. Lets Choi, his midfield general, run the show.
DescriptionJP: ファイアードラゴンの監督。 戦術は 司令塔のチャンスウに一任している。

Name: Freddy McQueen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A life of derring-do as a spy in MI6—that's this player's dream.
NameJP: フレディ・マックイーン
DescriptionJP: スパイに憧れ 将来は絶対 ＭＩ６に入ると 息巻いている。

Name: Jonny Gascoigne
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He might dress and act like a punk, but deep down he's a real softie.
NameJP: ジョニー・ガスコイン
DescriptionJP: パンク・ファッションが大好きだけど 実は気が弱い。

Name: David Buckingham
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This spendthrift can't resist any "by royal appointment" products.
NameJP: デービッド・バッキンガム
DescriptionJP: 王室御用達のものは何でも買ってしまう 王室マニア。

Name: Lance Rawton
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Clinging to the rights and privileges of the aristocracy, he asserts his right to lead.
DescriptionJP: 貴族としての義務にこだわり 人々のために率先して動く。

Name: Edge Ripper
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's already earned a cult following abroad as a heavy metal vocalist.
DescriptionJP: ヘヴィメタルのボーカリスト。 この歳で海外公演をするほどの人気。

Name: Peter Cole
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A music buff who insists that the British music scene is the best in the world.
DescriptionJP: イギリスの音楽業界についてなら 彼に聞くのが一番！

Name: Gary Mane
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He bakes a mean scone, which can form the centerpiece of even the poshest cream teas.
DescriptionJP: 彼の作ったスコーンは どんなイギリス紅茶にもぴったり！

Name: Paul Appleton
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd love to get the old band together for one last reunion, but the guys aren't having it.
NameJP: ポール・アップルトン
DescriptionJP: 歴史に残るバンドを結成したいと 思っているが メンバーが集まらない。

Name: Eric Purpleton
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Wimbledon was calling for this talented player, but an arm injury signaled a move to football.
NameJP: エリック・パープルトン
DescriptionJP: 末はウィンブルドンかと言われた テニスの名手。手首のケガでサッカーに。

Name: Edgar Partinus
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a calm and brave leader. He's popular, and always gives his best.
NameJP: エドガー・バルチナス
DescriptionJP: ファンに『静かなる闘将』と呼ばれている ナイツオブクィーンを率いるキャプテン。

Name: Phillip Owen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a master of English cuisine, and won't tolerate those who put it down.
NameJP: フィリップ・オーウェン
DescriptionJP: イギリス料理で成功して 絶対にまずいと言わせないようにしたい。

Name: Servilius Jeeves
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He was born into a long line of butlers, so he knows the finer points of entertaining guests.
DescriptionJP: 執事の家に生まれ 彼も人をもてなす名人に。

Name: Martin Squall
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An expert in equestrian matters, he's already raised a few Grand National winners!
NameJP: マーティン・スコール
DescriptionJP: 競走馬の世話がうまく 手がけた馬がダービーで優勝したことも！

Name: Nick Woodgate
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's seriously thinking about opening a school for wizards.
NameJP: ニック・ウッドゲート
DescriptionJP: イギリスで 魔法学校を開きたいと 真剣に思っている。

Name: Mikey Richards
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His hobby is tailoring suits, and no other junior high school student can touch his ability.
NameJP: マイキー・リチャーズ
DescriptionJP: スーツの知識と仕立ての技術で 彼を超える中学生はいない。

Name: Sirius Pounding
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player's rugby experience makes him prone to committing handballs.
DescriptionJP: ラグビーもうまいせいか 時々間違って 手でボールを触りそうになる。

Name: Aaron Adams
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Manager of the Queen's Knights. Known for his precise, elegant formation calls.
DescriptionJP: ナイツオブクィーンの監督。 巧みなフォーメーション指示を得意とする。

Name: Indigo Lazuli
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a strong sense of right and wrong. He only joined Team D to save his own hide.
DescriptionJP: 正義感あふれる人物だったが 生活のため やむなくチームＫに入った。

Name: Roseo Diamante
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He was born on the wrong side of the tracks, so he's determined to succeed in life.
NameJP: ロゼオ・ディアマンテ
DescriptionJP: 下町生まれのせいか 上昇志向が強い。

Name: Azubel Turchese
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's always trying to find a solution to the refuse problem in Naples.
NameJP: アズベル・トルケーゼ
DescriptionJP: ナポリのゴミ問題に いつも頭を悩ませている。

Name: Nello Agata
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He longed for the life of an urbanite, so he chose football to make a name for himself.
DescriptionJP: 都会の生活に憧れ サッカーで一旗揚げようとしている。

Name: Azzurro Zaffiro
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's active in organizations attempting to halt the sinking of Venice.
NameJP: アズロ・ザッフィーレ
DescriptionJP: ベネチアの水没をなんとか食い止めたいと 色々活動している。

Name: Beldio Smeraldo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player is livid about the damage done to Rome's architectural heritage by pollution.
NameJP: ベルディオ・ズメラルド
DescriptionJP: ローマの遺跡が 公害で損なわれていくのが 絶対に許せない。

Name: Rosso Granato
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a born aristocrat, but he's determined to do something worthwhile with his life.
DescriptionJP: 自分もイタリア貴族だが 貴族というだけで何もしないヤツが大嫌い。

Name: Giallo Topazio
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He dreams of being a great fashion designer some day, but so far he hasn't had much luck.
NameJP: ジャッロ・トパーツィオ
DescriptionJP: イタリアファッション界のトップを 目指しているのに 誰も認めてくれない。

Name: Bianco Perla
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's never even seen a bottle of wine, but he still dreams of becoming a sommelier.
DescriptionJP: ワインを飲んだことがないのに なぜか ソムリエ志望。

Name: Giulio Acuto
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: With the power given to him by Mister D, his speed and skill are unmatched.
NameJP: デモーニオ・ストラーダ
DescriptionJP: ミスターＫによって力を与えられた。 鬼道そっくりだが 本物以上の力を持つ。

Name: Violetto Ametista
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's arrogant and pushy, so the other players don't like him all that much.
NameJP: ビオレテ・アメティスタ
DescriptionJP: 押しが強いせいか みんなから嫌われている。

Name: Grigio Quarzo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd love to go on a date in Rome, but he keeps getting knocked back.
NameJP: グリッジョ・ジェッソ
DescriptionJP: ローマでおしゃれなデートをしたいが 相手がいない。

Name: Pardo Berillo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Initially he'd hoped to be an opera singer, but his vocal cords gave out.
DescriptionJP: オペラ歌手を目指していたが のどを痛めてサッカーに転向。

Name: Marrone Corniola
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He likes to make pizzas with wacky toppings, but they are mostly disgusting.
NameJP: マッローネ・ティタニート
DescriptionJP: 変なトッピングのピザばかり作るので みんなから避けられている。

Name: Amaranto Rubino
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: They laughed when he said he wanted to turn pro, but he's determined to laugh last.
NameJP: アマラント・ルビーノ
DescriptionJP: プロサッカー選手になると言ったら バカにされ 見返してやろうと奮闘中。

Name: Avorio Opale
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He hopes to be a model, but as yet he's still unrecognized in the fashion world.
NameJP: ラッティモ・オパーレ
DescriptionJP: イタリアトップモデルを目指し 下積み中。

Name: Mister D
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Ray Dark's alias. His true goal? To deny and destroy the very existence of football.
DescriptionJP: 影山零治の仮の姿。 その目的は すべてのサッカーの否定と破壊。

Name: Jorge Ortega
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's known for his aggressive style. His brutal tackles often lead to melees.
DescriptionJP: ゲリラ的な戦い方が得意で 混戦になるほど 生き生きとする。

Name: Thiago Torres
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He boasts of his Wall of Steel defence, and marshals his teammates from the back.
DescriptionJP: ジ・エンパイアのキャプテンでＤＦ。 『アンデスの不落の要塞』と呼ばれる。

Name: Julio Acosta
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a fondness for yerba maté tea, and he always packs some when he plays away.
DescriptionJP: マテ茶が大好きで 海外遠征のときも 必ず持っていく。

Name: Grande Díaz
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: From a family of vineyard owners, he's striving to put Argentinian wine on the map.
DescriptionJP: ワイン農家の子ども。アルゼンチンワインを 世界一にしようとがんばる。

Name: Ramón Martínez
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He really appreciates the colonial architecture of Buenos Aires.
DescriptionJP: ブエノスアイレスのヨーロッパ風建築を 見て歩くのが好き。

Name: Esteban Carlos
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He does altitude training in the Andes, so there's no escaping his tenacious plays.
NameJP: エステバン・カルロス
DescriptionJP: アンデス山脈で鍛えた足腰で 粘り強いプレイをする。

Name: Sergio Pérez
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has lofty ambitions of reinventing the Argentinian literary scene.
DescriptionJP: アルゼンチン文学の 新たなリーダーと なるべく いつも小説を書いている。

Name: Roberto Torres
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The old legend of El Dorado is an enduring passion for him. He dreams of finding it.
DescriptionJP: アンデスにあるという 幻の黄金都市を探している。

Name: Pablo Castillo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The natural beauty of Argentina inspires his art, and he hopes for recognition.
NameJP: パブロ・カスティーヨ
DescriptionJP: アルゼンチンの自然を絵に描いて 多くの人に見てもらいたい。

Name: Leone Badigo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His swooping, powerful plays have earned him the nickname El Cóndor.
DescriptionJP: パワフルで自在なプレイで 『エル・コンドル』と呼ばれている。

Name: Diego Oro
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This nutty player sets off fireworks in his bathroom at Christmas and new year.
DescriptionJP: クリスマスや正月には 室内でお祝いの花火！ちょっと危ない。

Name: Lionel Cruz
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He makes incredible pork sausages. It's like a hobby for him.
DescriptionJP: 豚肉ソーセージを作る名人。 休みの日は いつもソーセージ作り。

Name: Mario Saviola
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His pushy parents said to him, "you'd better win, or else!" which caused him much angst.
DescriptionJP: 熱狂的なサッカーファンの父に 「負けたら 帰ってくるな」と言われ ビビっている。

Name: Hernán Tévez
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Despite his young age, he helps out at the local radio station, covering football matches.
DescriptionJP: この歳で 地元ラジオ局の サッカー中継を 手伝っている。

Name: Herman Samuel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Serve him a steak, sprinkled with sea salt and grilled over an open fire, and he's in heaven.
DescriptionJP: 牛肉を塩だけで金網で焼いて食べるのが 大好物。

Name: Ricardo Agüero
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The windy regions of Patagonia have been his training ground, so he's an all-weather player.
DescriptionJP: パタゴニアの強風地帯で特訓して どんな風にも負けなくなった。

Name: Daniel Sturbin
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Manager of The Empire. His defenses are called unbreakable fortresses.
NameJP: ダニエル・スタービン
DescriptionJP: ジ・エンパイアの監督。 強力な守備を武器に 不落の要塞を築く。

Name: Billy Dash
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wants to be a cowboy in a western. He's always practicing lines in the mirror.
DescriptionJP: 西部劇ショーの花形ガンマンを目指し 鏡の前で日夜 華麗なガン捌きを特訓中。

Name: Ted Bryant
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He sees Silicon Valley as a goldmine, and he hopes to make his fortune there.
DescriptionJP: シリコンバレーでＩＴ企業を立ち上げて 世界中を飛び回る 億万長者になるのが夢。

Name: Tony Strider
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This guy is obsessed with eating steaks. He can't rest unless he eats one a day.
NameJP: トニー・ストライダス
DescriptionJP: 分厚いステーキを食べるのが大好きで １日１枚は食べないと気が済まない。

Name: Drake Dynamo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: They say that he once wrestled a buffalo to the ground. I'm not so sure, though.
DescriptionJP: バッファローを素手でねじ伏せた伝説を持つ。 額の傷は 壮絶な戦いの証。

Name: Bobby Shearer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Despite his somewhat frivolous nature, he has a warm heart and genuinely cares for his friends.
DescriptionJP: 軽いノリだが その心は熱く 仲間を思う気持ちは人一倍。

Name: Steve Woodmark
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His ambition is to sit in the Oval Office, but no one takes him seriously.
NameJP: スティーブ・ウッドマック
DescriptionJP: 将来の夢はアメリカ大統領！ 誰も本気にしてくれないが 絶対に諦めない。

Name: Erik Eagle
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An all-rounder once lauded as a genius. A powerhouse up front and a wall in the back.
DescriptionJP: かつては天才と呼ばれた万能プレイヤー。 前線だけでなく守りにも気を配る。

Name: Shane Pierce
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's only young, but he has a good grasp of Wall Street's complex financial structures.
DescriptionJP: 金融ビジネスのすべてを理解した 若き天才。 既に 莫大な資産を持っているとか。

Name: Mark Krueger
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Captain and ace of Team America. Together with Dylan, they light up the field.
DescriptionJP: キャプテンを務める アメリカのスター選手。 ディランとのコンビネーションで魅せる。

Name: Dylan Keats
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His exploits in the North American qualifiers earned him the nickname Hat-Trick Kid.
DescriptionJP: アメリカ代表チームの点取り屋。 『ミスターゴール』と呼ばれているらしい。

Name: Gabriel Jax
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's one of those Hollywood child stars. Let's hope his success continues.
NameJP: ミケーレ・ジャックス
DescriptionJP: ハリウッド俳優歴１０年の天才子役。 フィールドでもステージでも観客を魅了する。

Name: Alex Hawke
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He insists that he can read the signs in nature to predict the weather.
DescriptionJP: 自然と語らい 天気を予測できると言い張る。 何でも 風が答えてくれるのだとか。

Name: Corey Washington
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wants to live the American dream by taking his country all the way to the top.
DescriptionJP: サッカーでアメリカンドリームを 実現させようとがんばっている。

Name: Bob Bobbins
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a real slob. He loves to sprawl on the sofa, swilling cola and chomping chips.
DescriptionJP: ポテトチップとコーラを片手に ビデオばかり見ているカウチ族。

Name: Petie Pooma
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's tiny for an American, but within him hides the coiled power of a jungle cat.
DescriptionJP: アメリカではあまり多くない小柄な体だが それをバネにしてがんばっている。

Name: Norbert Poindexter
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He didn't care much for American football, but he really took to soccer.
DescriptionJP: アメフトでは挫折を経験したが 素早さを活かし サッカーに転向して成功！

Name: Mac Scryde
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Manager of Unicorn. Tough as nails but truly cares for his players.
DescriptionJP: ユニコーンの監督。 責任感が強く 選手思いの一面がある。

Name: Gigi Blasi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's the best goalie in Italy, so you can count on his saves.
DescriptionJP: イタリア代表 オルフェウスのＧＫ。 『イタリア最強の守護神』の異名を持つ。

Name: Vento Galliano
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He takes exquisite care of his personal style, even wearing tailored boxers.
DescriptionJP: 目立たない部分に人一倍気を遣う 真のおしゃれ。

Name: Ottorino Nobili
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Can spin out the perfect pizza dough with sheer force.
NameJP: オットリーノ・ノビリ
DescriptionJP: そのパワーで ピザ生地を見事に作っちゃう。

Name: Anton Graziuso
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This plucky chap hopes to join the police and take on the criminal underworld.
NameJP: アントン・ガッツーゾ
DescriptionJP: 警察官になって 悪の組織と戦いたいという夢がある。

Name: Marco Maserati
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: If it's a pasta-based dish you're after, ask this guy! He's very proud of his regional cuisine.
NameJP: マルコ・マセラッティ
DescriptionJP: パスタ料理なら任せとけ。 生地から自分で作っちゃう！

Name: Angelo Gabrini
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's already won many awards for artisanship, as a crafter of cameo brooches.
NameJP: アンジェロ・ガブリーニ
DescriptionJP: 天使のように愛くるしい容姿のＭＦ。 実は 何度も賞をもらっているカメオ職人。

Name: Gianluca Zanardi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He works as a gondolier in Venice to improve his strength and balance.
NameJP: ジャンルカ・ザナルディ
DescriptionJP: 一流のゴンドラの漕ぎ手になるべく ベニスで今日も特訓中。

Name: Giorgio Giannini
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's from a well-established family, but he's not one to rest on his laurels.
NameJP: ジョルジョ・ジャンニーニ
DescriptionJP: 名家でありながら その地位に あぐらをかかない 真の貴族。

Name: Dante Diavolo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's always riding his bike. He hopes to represent Italy as a cyclist.
DescriptionJP: 自転車レースでイタリア代表になるため 今日も漕ぎまくる！

Name: Paolo Bianchi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Orpheus's ace striker known as the White Comet of Italy.
NameJP: フィディオ・アルデナ
DescriptionJP: 『イタリアの白い流星』と呼ばれている オルフェウスのエースストライカー。

Name: Raffaele Generani
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Even though he's still in junior high, he's getting a nice income from modelling.
NameJP: ラファエレ・ジェネラーニ
DescriptionJP: 中学生なのに すでにトップモデルとなっている。

Name: Daniele Sanctis
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Everyone loves this chilled-out guy from down south for his laid-back charm.
NameJP: ダニエレ・サンクティス
DescriptionJP: 南部生まれでのんびり屋。 でもみんなから好かれている。

Name: Enrico Oliviero
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His passion is fashion design. He's already worked up a stylish take on his team's kit.
DescriptionJP: 服の一流デザイナーを目指し まずは チームのユニフォームから。

Name: Alessandro Rossa
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: You can see your face in the fine Italian leather of this lad's shoes.
NameJP: アレサンドロ・ロッサ
DescriptionJP: イタリア革靴を上品に磨かせたら ナンバーワン！

Name: Giuseppe Cannavaro
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Fascinated by the ruins of Pompeii, he spends his Saturdays helping out on digs.
NameJP: ジュゼッペ・カンナバロ
DescriptionJP: ポンペイ遺跡に興味があって いつか発掘隊に参加したい。

Name: Falcão Da Silva
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He trained his reflexes in the depths of the Amazon, and puts them to work on the pitch.
NameJP: ファルカオ・ダシウバ
DescriptionJP: アマゾンの奥地で鍛えられた 野生の反応で ボールをゲット！

Name: Carlos Lagarto
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He seems to move to a samba rhythm when he makes a challenge on the pitch.
NameJP: ラガルート・カルロス
DescriptionJP: サンバのリズム感で 相手ボールを見事に奪い取る。

Name: Antonio Bagre
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's involved in an environmental movement to save the endangered Brazilwood tree.
NameJP: バーグレ・アントニオ
DescriptionJP: ブラジルボクという絶滅しかかっている木を 復活させようとしている。

Name: Monstro Ximenes
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: When he drinks coffee, he surges with power. Doesn't do his health much good, though.
DescriptionJP: コーヒーを飲むとパワー３倍に！ ただ 胃はちょっともたれ気味。

Name: Formiga Clemens
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He likes to pioneer forms of agriculture that are more rainforest friendly.
NameJP: フォルミガ・クレメンス
DescriptionJP: 焼き畑に頼らない しっかりとした農業を やりたいと思っている。

Name: Presa Passos
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's really interested in developing engine fuel derived from sugar cane.
DescriptionJP: サトウキビを使って ガソリンの代わりになる研究を手伝っている。

Name: Borboleta Barboza
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wants to look beyond the borders of Brazil and study the playing styles of other nations.
NameJP: ボルボレタ・バルボッサ
DescriptionJP: 世界を回って ブラジル以外の サッカープレイも取り入れたいと思っている。

Name: Coruja Cerezo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His powerful physique is down to his arduous training carrying bundles of sugar cane.
DescriptionJP: サトウキビを運んで鍛えた足腰は 誰にも負けない！

Name: Leonardo Almeida
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Football's in his blood. He's the fourth generation to represent his country.
NameJP: レオナルド・アルメイダ
DescriptionJP: ひいおじいちゃんの代から みんなブラジル代表という サッカー一族。

Name: Mac Robingo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Captain of Brazil's national team, The Kingdom. Nicknamed the Goal King.
DescriptionJP: 『キングオブファンタジスタ』と呼ばれる ブラジル代表 ザ・キングダムのキャプテン。

Name: Gato Carvalho
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: At the carnival, listen out for the distinctive timbre of his home-made tambourine.
DescriptionJP: 彼の作ったタンバリンは 音色が最高で カーニバルで大人気！

Name: Xavier Ribeiro
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's always thinking up spectacular outfits to wear to the carnival.
NameJP: シャバリー・リベイロ
DescriptionJP: カーニバルで 誰もが驚くような姿を いつも考えている。

Name: Ulisses Nogueira
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His cool and calculated style doesn't always mesh with passionate Latin football.
DescriptionJP: 冷静なチームプレイを目指す彼の考えは 南米スタイルと合わないことも。

Name: Gervasio Oliveira
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His big plan is to start an international biofuel business in Brazil.
NameJP: カバーロ・オリビエラ
DescriptionJP: ブラジルで起業して 世界にはばたける バイオプラントを起こすのが夢。

Name: Tigre Mendes
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He gets more and more pumped as the crowd cheer louder and louder!
DescriptionJP: 熱狂的な応援を受けるほど パワーを発揮する。

Name: Grillo Santos
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His family runs a traditional Brazilian eatery, so he's always cooking for his teammates.
DescriptionJP: ブラジル料理のお店の息子。 チームの料理は彼が作っているとか。

Name: Leão Samus
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Former Kingdom manager, ousted by Zoolan.
DescriptionJP: ザ・キングダムの前監督。 ガルシルドに監督の座を奪われた。

Name: Zoolan Rice
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The Kingdom's new manager, a wealthy oil magnate with global reach.
NameJP: ガルシルド・ベイハン
DescriptionJP: ザ・キングダムの新監督。 油田を所有し 世界の経済を掌握している。

Name: Cyril Fox
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He struggled to read his rivals' intentions, but he's getting there with Zoolan Rice's guidance.
DescriptionJP: 相手のウラを読むのが苦手だったのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Jacques Allemand
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Zoolan Rice has been teaching him how to play dirty. It's a contact sport after all.
DescriptionJP: ダーティなプレイができなかったのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Phil A. Minion
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a bit podgy, but a sharp guy. Be very wary of his disarming grin.
NameJP: ラボック・ヘンクタッカー
DescriptionJP: チーム・ガルシルドで一番のキレ者。 常に不敵な笑みを浮かべる不気味なＤＦだ。

Name: Buddy Plains
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He used to back out of challenges for fear of injury, but Zoolan Rice helped him improve.
DescriptionJP: ケガを恐れて相手に突っ込めなかったのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Dean Goddard
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He was no good at teamwork, but Zoolan Rice kicked him into touch.
DescriptionJP: チームプレイが苦手だったところを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Cecil Crowley
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wasn't able to see very well in the daytime, but Zoolan Rice soon fixed that.
DescriptionJP: 視力が弱っていたところを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Seth Hedges
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He was weak against opponents' attacks, but Zoolan Rice helped him overcome that.
DescriptionJP: 相手の攻撃に弱かったところを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Niccolo Mantegna
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His technique was lacking in edge, but Zoolan Rice soon sorted that out.
DescriptionJP: 技に切れ味がなかったところを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Damien Crawford
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Team Zoolan's leader on the pitch. He's also known by the ominous name Grim Reaper.
DescriptionJP: チームガルシルドの司令塔。 『死神』と呼ばれ嫌われた過去を持つ。

Name: Avinash Chowdhury
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd lost confidence, and didn't know how to get it back. Until he met Zoolan Rice, that is...
DescriptionJP: 適応力が弱くて伸びなやんでいたのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Sedgley Scofield
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His power to make decisive attacks was greatly boosted by Zoolan Rice.
DescriptionJP: 決定的な一撃の力に欠けていたのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Grizzler Bruin
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd lacked precision on the pitch, but thanks to Zoolan Rice, he's like a laser now.
DescriptionJP: プレイに正確さが欠けていたのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Ian C. Wincy
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Physically, he was weak till Zoolan Rice turbocharged him. Now he's built like a tank.
DescriptionJP: フィジカル面が弱かったのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Bandy Horsman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His resolve on the pitch was weak, but Zoolan Rice gifted him a steady nerve.
DescriptionJP: プレイに安定感が欠けていたのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Ali Caiman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player's unpolished ball skills were improved by Zoolan Rice.
DescriptionJP: コントロール力の甘さを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Chris Ellis
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He didn't have much stamina until Zoolan Rice supercharged him.
DescriptionJP: スタミナが不足していたのを ガルシルドによって改造された。

Name: Hector Helio
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Captain and keeper of the Little Gigantes, raised deep in Côte-Victoire's countryside.
DescriptionJP: リトルギガントのキャプテンでＧＫ。 コトアールという国の田舎で育った。

Name: Hector Helio
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A Victoirean boy from out in the sticks. It's already clear that he has incredible potential.
DescriptionJP: コトアールの田舎の少年。 無限の可能性を秘めている。

Name: Zephyr Vitesse
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Hector's old friend. He rushes like a gale-force wind to mark his opponents.
NameJP: ウィンディ・ファスタ
DescriptionJP: 風のようなスピードで相手をマーク！ ロココの幼なじみ。

Name: Walter Mountain
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Despite providing a solid defence, he's a massive glutton and a bit of scaredy-cat.
NameJP: ウォルター・マウンテン
DescriptionJP: そのディフェンスは まさにウォール。 しかし 臆病かつ食いしんぼうな性格だ。

Name: Jimi Gaines
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wears sunglasses to try to stand out, but they make him look a bit creepy.
DescriptionJP: 目立つためにサングラスをかけたら みんなに怖がられるはめに。

Name: Ian Ferrum
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He packs a lot of guts in that small frame! When things heat up he's right there.
DescriptionJP: 小さいけれどガッツは十分！ やる時はやるでやんす！

Name: Quint Hampton
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He thought he'd try a perm, but he still doesn't make much of an impression.
DescriptionJP: 個性を出すためにパーマをかけたら なんだか中途ハンパに。

Name: Yasir Haddad
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player uses karate techniques to snatch away the ball! Hi-YAH!
DescriptionJP: 空手で鍛えた足技で ボールを奪うぞ！ セイヤッ！

Name: Keith Ryan
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's forever fiddling with his afro, and truth be told, he's a bit of a coward.
DescriptionJP: いつもチーム内でアフロをいじられる。 実は臆病な性格。

Name: Maximino Cruz
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's rather fickle. His teammates worry that he'll get tired of football.
DescriptionJP: 飽きっぽい性格なので いつサッカーに飽きるか 周りはヒヤヒヤ。

Name: Gareth Flare
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An ace striker from Côte-Victoire. He's always looking out for his sister.
DescriptionJP: コトアールの天才ストライカー。 妹をとても大事にしているらしい。

Name: Drago Hill
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A Côte-Victoire striker. He nurses a rivalry with Gareth Flare.
DescriptionJP: コトアールのストライカー。 ゴーシュにライバル心を抱いている。

Name: Keenan DiFortune
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's known Hector for a long time, and he really looks up to him.
DescriptionJP: ロココの幼なじみ。 ロココをとても尊敬している。

Name: Jarell Mangrove
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This prankster will snatch away the ball while you're not looking.
NameJP: マッコール・キサッラ
DescriptionJP: イタズラ大好き！ あっという間にボールを奪い去る。

Name: Vic Vitrum
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a keen eye for enemy strategies, so his teammates often consult him on tactics.
DescriptionJP: 相手チームの分析ならお任せ！ 別名ウンチクくん。

Name: Li Leung
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A popular, happy-go-lucky player who is deceptively strong on the pitch.
DescriptionJP: 甘いマスクの人気者。 顔に似合わず そのプレイは強力。

Name: Jazzy Hedgeer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A southern surf dude with boundless enthusiasm, and a natty sun visor.
DescriptionJP: 南の国のノリノリ選手。 今日もサンバイザーがまぶしいぜ！

Name: David Arrows
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Manager of the Little Gigantes, driven to raise the ultimate team.
DescriptionJP: リトルギガントの監督。 最強のチームの育成に 自分のすべてを注ぐ。

Name: Roger Pialat
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player from Montmartre is always creating football-themed paintings.
DescriptionJP: モンマルトルで いつも絵を描いている。 サッカー画のパイオニアと呼ばれたい。

Name: Kevin Pinot
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's currently trying to adapt Napoleonic tactics for the football pitch.
DescriptionJP: ナポレオンの作戦を サッカーに応用できないかと研究している。

Name: Michaël Aron
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Despite his appearance, he's a master of subtle French cuisine.
DescriptionJP: こんな顔をしているけど 繊細なフランス料理を作れるんだ。

Name: Francis Poujol
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He dreams of building an iconic structure one day, like the Eiffel Tower or Arc de Triomphe.
DescriptionJP: いつかパリに エッフェル塔や凱旋門よりも 有名な建物をつくりたい！

Name: Pierre Godin
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His motto is to always play with style and grace, whoever you're up against.
DescriptionJP: どんなハードな試合でも 常にプレイは美しく がモットー。

Name: Roland Pérec
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He spends his free time watching the world go by in Parisian-style café society.
DescriptionJP: 休みの日には いつも屋外のカフェで のんびりしている。

Name: Julien Rousseau
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He likes to play with a rose clamped between his teeth. How very pretentious.
DescriptionJP: 常にバラの花をくわえてプレイするという ローズグリフォンを率いるキャプテン。

Name: Stéphane Hinault
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This young man is already a hitmaker in the world of French music.
DescriptionJP: シャンソンの若き天才アーティスト。 すべての曲が大ヒット！

Name: Romuald Huysmans
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: France's number one model in his age group. He's in demand for photos and shows.
DescriptionJP: フランス一の少年モデル。 ショーにグラビアにと引っ張りだこ。

Name: Jérôme Hervaud
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: With his subtle sense of smell, he's able to blend the ideal perfume for any given person.
DescriptionJP: 鋭い嗅覚で その人にベストの香水をブレンドできる。

Name: Alain Favreau
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The son of a bicycle repairman. He'd like to help out at the Tour de France one day.
DescriptionJP: 自転車整備士の息子。 いつかロードレースのサポーターになりたい。

Name: Émile Lazare
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a connoisseur of French cinema, with a huge DVD collection.
DescriptionJP: フランス映画は すべてＤＶＤを 持っているという 映画マニア。

Name: André Pinson
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's well read in continental philosophy, but his friends rarely know what he's on about.
DescriptionJP: フランス哲学を勉強しているけど さすがに友だちは理解できない。

Name: Jean Gutain
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A self-styled fashion prodigy. However, he hasn't really proved himself yet.
DescriptionJP: 自称天才ファッションデザイナー。 でもちょっと先を行きすぎているかも。

Name: Claude Moreau
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: People come from all over France to try his delicious baguettes.
DescriptionJP: 彼の焼いたバゲットを求めて フランス全土から集まってくるとか。

Name: Michel Morland
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: When it comes to tending vineyards, he's got green fingers for sure.
DescriptionJP: ワイン用のぶどうの世話をやらせたら 天才的。

Name: Fermín Sánchez
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Like a bull at a matador, he charges straight through the crowd to grab the ball.
NameJP: フェルミン・サンチェス
DescriptionJP: 闘牛の牛のように ボールをキープするために一直線に突き進む。

Name: José Costa
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's an experienced and tenacious mountain biker.
DescriptionJP: 自転車の山登りなら誰にも負けない ヒルクライマー！

Name: Rafael López
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a great flamenco dancer. Girls are lining up for a chance to dance with him.
DescriptionJP: フラメンコダンスの達人。 彼と踊りたい人たちが列を作ってるとか！？

Name: Antonio Gallego
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's always making sketches for abstract paintings, like Picasso.
NameJP: アントニオ・ガリウス
DescriptionJP: ピカソに負けない抽象画を描こうと いつもスケッチを欠かさない。

Name: Queraldo Naval
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's trained to be a matador since he was a child, but he hates hurting animals.
DescriptionJP: 闘牛のマタドール目指して 幼いころから特訓してきた。

Name: Juan Nadal
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He eats five meals a day to keep his strength up when he's travelling overseas.
DescriptionJP: 海外に行っても １日５回の食事をしないとパワーが出ない。

Name: Igor Ferreira
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's an avid consumer of paella, but he's really fussy about the type of rice.
DescriptionJP: パエリアが大好き。米も スペイン米でなければ納得しないこだわり。

Name: Pedro Moreno
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's raising a black Iberian pig at home, in the hope of producing tasty ham.
DescriptionJP: イベリコ豚を家で育てている。 おいしいハムができるかな？

Name: Miguel Pereira
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His hobby is making model sailing boats. He's assembling an invincible armada in his bathtub.
DescriptionJP: 帆船の模型を作って 家に無敵艦隊を再現している。

Name: Samuel Mayo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This plucky Pamplonica dreams of one day showing his mettle at the Running of the Bulls.
DescriptionJP: 牛追い祭りで 牛と真っ向から 勝負したという伝説の持ち主。

Name: Davi Peroqué
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's fiercely proud of Spanish football, and doesn't hide his desire to take on the world.
DescriptionJP: スペインサッカーに誇りを持っていて 国外では対抗意識むき出しに。

Name: Juan Espindola
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Everyone is bewitched by his virtuosic skill at flamenco guitar.
NameJP: フアン・スベルディア
DescriptionJP: フラメンコギターの天才。 華麗なテクニックに みんなうっとり。

Name: Isaac César
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An opportunist on and off the pitch. If he sees a beautiful girl, he'll try to charm her.
DescriptionJP: 美人を見つけると 必ずナンパしようとする。 たとえ対戦相手でも！

Name: Laudelino Castor
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Like Don Quixote, he acts rashly without considering consequences.
NameJP: ラウデリーノ・サストレ
DescriptionJP: ドン・キホーテのように 後先をあまり考えずにプレイしてしまう。

Name: Carlos Arroyo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He hopes to raise architectural wonders like the Sagrada Familia.
DescriptionJP: サグラダ・ファミリアに負けない 大建築物を建てるのが夢。

Name: Federico Rubiera
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd like to have a go at synchronized swimming, but he can't find a boys' team.
NameJP: フェデリコ・ルビエラ
DescriptionJP: アーティスティックスイミングが やりたいのに 男子チームがなくてがっかり。

Name: Thorsten Welger
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His family are brewers, but he prefers a nice glass of Apfelschorle.
NameJP: トルステン・ベルガー
DescriptionJP: 家族でビール造りをしている。 自分が造ったビールが飲めないのは残念。

Name: Alexander Hausen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player always acts logically, no matter what kind of situation he's in.
NameJP: アレクサンダー・ハウゼン
DescriptionJP: どれだけ混乱した状況でも いつも合理的な行動をとる。

Name: Heinrich Farber
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Because of his strange hobby of sharpening knives, he is often mistaken for a baddy.
NameJP: ハインリヒ・フリッツ
DescriptionJP: 刃物を研ぐのが趣味。 でもその姿は アブない人とよく間違われる。

Name: Kurt Zawel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: If he doesn't get his daily portion of Kartoffelsalat, he's got no energy.
DescriptionJP: ジャガイモを毎日食べないと 実力が発揮できない。

Name: Lukas Schmidt
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves tanks, so he's taking a tour of all the tank museums in Europe.
DescriptionJP: 戦車が大好き。 ヨーロッパ中の戦車博物館を巡っている。

Name: Theodor Ulrich
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: With a civilized demeanor and an iron will, he's the model of a German sportsman.
NameJP: テオドール・ウルリッヒ
DescriptionJP: 鋼鉄の意志と紳士な態度を貫く ドイツ人プレイヤーの鑑。

Name: Jan Oster
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This keen amateur mechanic is lucky enough to hail from the home of precision engineering.
DescriptionJP: ドイツの技術は世界一！と信じて みんなにドイツ製品を勧める。

Name: Niklas Kuster
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A brutal player, he's able to overwhelm his rivals with constant attacks.
DescriptionJP: 相手ラインを突破するスピードから 『電撃戦のニクラス』とあだ名が。

Name: Jonas Polk
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He hopes to fly to Mars in a rocket of his own design one day.
DescriptionJP: いつか自分の造ったロケットで 有人火星飛行にいくのが夢。

Name: Maximilian Müller
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A proud Frankfurter who will never reveal his family's secret mix of seven herbs.
NameJP: マキシミリアン・ミラツ
DescriptionJP: ドイツワインが世界一だと言ってるが どこのワインも飲んだことはない。

Name: Peter Naumann
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's often seen in the park, reading from a volume of Heinrich Heine's poetry.
DescriptionJP: ドイツの詩を愛していて いつもハイネの詩集を持ち歩いている。

Name: Gerhard Enders
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He can't wait to pass his test and get behind the wheel of a smart German motor.
NameJP: ゲラルト・エンダース
DescriptionJP: ドイツの車が大好きで 免許を取ったら すぐにでもドイツ車に乗るつもり。

Name: Erwin Völz
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's deeply concerned about environmental issues, and always acts accordingly.
DescriptionJP: エコに誰よりも関心があって いつも地球にやさしい行動を心がけている。

Name: Jens Hoffman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's studying at music school in the hopes of surpassing Beethoven.
DescriptionJP: ベートーベンを超える作曲家を目指し 音楽学校で勉強中。

Name: Ernst Fliedner
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's from Bremen, but is driven to distraction by caterwauling farm animals.
NameJP: エルンスト・フロデノ
DescriptionJP: ブレーメン生まれ。いいところなのに 音楽隊のことしか聞かれないのが不満。

Name: Emmanuel Ewerz
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An accomplished sausage maker who keeps his team well supplied with protein.
NameJP: マヌエル・エーヴェルス
DescriptionJP: ソーセージ作りの名人。 チームのパワーの元は 彼のソーセージ？

Name: Zolani Baloi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He thinks his life is so interesting that he'd like to make a documentary about it.
DescriptionJP: 自分たちの生活に根ざした ドキュメンタリーＴＶを作りたい。

Name: Dakarai Furman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: On the pitch, he entrusts his movements to instinct, and the rhythm of nature.
NameJP: ディンガ・フィグラン
DescriptionJP: 自然と湧き上がってくる体のリズムに 身を任せてプレイする。

Name: Jake Fana
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He thinks there might be a future in the diamond processing industry.
DescriptionJP: ダイヤモンドの原石を 自分たちで ちゃんと磨きたいと思っている。

Name: Masego Molelo
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's interested in stocks and shares, so he's boning up on all that stuff now.
DescriptionJP: 証券業界に興味があって 色々と勉強中。

Name: Cassius Tobler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wants to find a way to combine both instinct and scientific reasoning.
DescriptionJP: 野生のカンと科学的な理論を 結びつけようと奮闘中。

Name: Anton Nortje
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His signature move is an all-or-nothing charge that he perfected playing rugby.
DescriptionJP: ラグビーで鍛えたタックル力で 一気にチャージ！

Name: Adam Marunga
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player hopes that football can become a tool to end racial discrimination.
DescriptionJP: 人種差別は絶対に許さない。 世界平和をサッカーで！

Name: Reggie Ines
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's taking a stand against the illegal hunting of wild pachyderms.
DescriptionJP: 野生のゾウの保護を手伝って 悪いハンターと戦っている。

Name: Siyabonga Mahlangu
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His ambition is to sail around the world on a boat that he made himself.
DescriptionJP: 自分の造った船で 世界一周したいと思っている。

Name: Nathan Tswane
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He lets an ostrich chase him to train his legs and balance.
DescriptionJP: ダチョウと競争しながら 足腰を鍛えている。

Name: Melisizwe Zamani
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He says that mutton is a versatile and delicious meat, and won't hear otherwise.
DescriptionJP: ヒツジの肉で いろんな料理を作れる。 臭くないよ！

Name: Herschel De Villiers
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has an affinity with wild beasts. They say he once rode on a lion's back.
NameJP: ヘゼキエル・デビリアズ
DescriptionJP: 野生動物の心が分かるらしい。 ライオンにまたがったという伝説も！

Name: Moeneeb Booysen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: In order to tackle global warming, this player plants new trees.
DescriptionJP: 地球温暖化を防ごうと 木を植えて緑を取り戻そうとしている。

Name: Kennedy McCarthy
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wants to find a gold mine and get rich quick, but he has no idea where to start.
NameJP: ケネデ・ムロベッヅィ
DescriptionJP: 金鉱を見つけて大金持ちになりたい！ でも 見つけ方を分かってない。

Name: Hugh Makebe
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has to be supplied with rooibos tea, or he gets anxious.
DescriptionJP: ルイボスティーというお茶を飲まないと 落ち着かない。

Name: Themba Sepeng
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wants to grow South African flowers, and share them with the world.
DescriptionJP: アフリカの美しい花を育てて 世界に届けたい！

Name: Anorel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He seems to be able to harness supernatural powers using mushrooms.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 そのパワーの源は やはりキノコらしい。

Name: Nenel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This heavenly player need only close his eyes to see the truth.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 瞳を静かに閉じて 真実を見抜くという。

Name: Genel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He is gifted with a supernatural bulk, with which he blasts away his foes.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 その巨体であらゆる悪を弾き飛ばす。

Name: Ekadel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Sanctus's cool lieutenant has magical gifts of his own, so watch out.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 セインの参謀役で 常にクールに振る舞う。

Name: Lephiel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This odd, slippery character has obtained the power of the heavens.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 飄々としていて 掴みどころのない性格。

Name: Sachinel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has magical power, but at heart he's a joker who loves to entertain.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 人を笑わせることが大好き。

Name: Wenel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A player with the power of the heavens. A cool lone wolf.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 無口でクールな 一匹オオカミタイプだ。

Name: Ientel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's got supernatural powers, but she'll win anyone over with her bright personality.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 明るい性格で みんなに慕われている。

Name: Nuel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This chap's magical powers come in useful on the pitch, and all the girls love him.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 キュートなルックスで女性にモテモテ。

Name: Gaiel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This kind, angelic player turns frightening when she gets angry.
DescriptionJP: 天界の力を受けつぐ 天空の使徒の一員。 普段は優しいのだが 怒ると怖いらしい。

Name: Sanctus
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The proud leader of Apostles from the Sky. He rules with a cool head.
DescriptionJP: 誇り高き 天空の使徒のリーダーでＦＷ。 冷徹なまでに 自身の『使命』にこだわる。

Name: Astaroth
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A player from the underworld. Some say his eyes can see the future.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 この世のすべてを見通す目を持つという。

Name: Bael
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Wielding dark powers, this player has a conceited and malevolent demeanor.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 邪悪な性格で 容赦なく相手を突き飛ばす。

Name: Abigor
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Using his dark abilities, this player is able to trace and predict the path of the ball.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 ボールの軌道を見抜くことができる。

Name: Behemoth
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A player from the underworld. The size of his body matches his greed.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 かなりの巨体で どん欲にボールを狙う。

Name: Belial
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He uses his magic powers to clearly perceive the dark underbelly of the world.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 その目は 何もかもを諦めている…。

Name: Malphas
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This devilish player enjoys deceiving his enemies with cruel lies.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 世にも残酷なウソで 相手を騙して喜ぶ。

Name: Glasya
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player combines magic power, sharp intelligence and untempered cruelty.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 知識と残酷さを兼ね備えている。

Name: Jezebeth
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player harnesses dark forces to communicate with the animal world.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 動物の言葉を理解できる。

Name: Arachne
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Using dark powers on the pitch, she inspires fear with her spider-like movements.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 クモのように機敏な動きで前線へ上がる。

Name: Thanatos
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A player from the underworld. The proud owner of an astronomical ego.
DescriptionJP: 魔界の力を受けつぐ 魔界軍団Ｚの一員。 『魔界最強』を豪語するストライカーだ。

Name: Destra
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: The cruel leader of Devil Army Z. Favorite dish: revenge, served cold.
DescriptionJP: 悪魔のように残酷な魔界軍団Ｚのリーダー。 彼の好物は 『人間の魂』なのだという。

Name: Lars Luceafăr
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Team Ogre's wall of a keeper, never seen without Lump and Bump on his shoulders.
DescriptionJP: 鉄壁の守りを誇るオーガのキーパー。 いつも両肩にゲボーとブボーを乗せている。

Name: Lump Trungus
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Elder twin with a + mark on his forehead, known for his monosyllabic laughter.
DescriptionJP: 額に＋の印がある ブボーの双子の兄。 なぜか「ゲゲゲゲ…！」としか喋らない。

Name: Bump Trungus
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Younger twin with a - mark on his forehead, known for his monosyllabic grunts.
DescriptionJP: 額に－の印がある ゲボーの双子の弟。 なぜか「ブブブブ…！」としか喋らない。

Name: Oni Triumvir
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: With his army training, he always keeps a watchful eye on the enemy.
DescriptionJP: 軍で培った兵士の教えを重んじており 常にチームの状況を把握して行動している。

Name: Drachen Gunther
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Anyone he fixes with his fearful gaze becomes paralyzed with horror.
NameJP: ドラッヘ・ギュンター
DescriptionJP: その迫力ある顔でニラみつけられた者は 恐怖のあまり 立ちすくんでしまうという。

Name: Mystral Callous
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He might look like a girl, but his style of play is surprisingly savage.
NameJP: ミストレーネ・カルス
DescriptionJP: 端正な顔立ちだが 内面は非常に攻撃的。 プライドが高く 何に対しても最高を目指す。

Name: Radd Ischer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: With his rotund body, he flicks away any kind of shot with ease.
DescriptionJP: その類いまれなる巨体で どんなシュートも弾き飛ばす。

Name: Escavan Malice
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's so hot-blooded, if a chance on goal is stolen from him, he flies into a rage.
DescriptionJP: 血の気が多いキケンなストライカー。 シュートチャンスを奪われると激怒する。

Name: Bash Lancer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Team Ogre's strongest soldier, he crushes his enemies with a cool smile.
DescriptionJP: オーガのキャプテンを務める最強の兵士。 クールな笑みを浮かべて 周りを圧倒する。

Name: Ichabod Stark
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His personality, his playing style, his face... It's all so spiky.
DescriptionJP: 見た目にとどまらず 性格やプレイなど すべての要素が鋭く尖っている。

Name: Jynx Jenkins
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has an ominous aura. Not even his teammates are sure of his past.
DescriptionJP: ブキミな雰囲気の選手。 その過去はチームメイトすら知らない。

Name: Canon Evans
Description: Mark's great-grandson, a fiery kid from eighty years in the future. Born to love football.
DescriptionJP: ８０年後の未来からやってきた円堂のひ孫。 未来のサッカーを愛する 熱血少年だ。

Name: Lucia
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Young girl who became able to see again thanks to Ray Dark. She admires her benefactor and can't wait to meet him again.
DescriptionJP: かつて 影山の支援で盲目を克服した少女。 影山を慕い 彼との再会を待ち望んでいる。

Name: Percy Verens
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Once he's locked on to his opponent, he pursues them doggedly.
DescriptionJP: 狙った相手を しつこく追いかけて 絶対に外さない。

Name: Bishop Carver
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His hobby is making chess pieces, and he dreams of a career as an artisan.
DescriptionJP: 将棋のコマを手作りしている。 将来はコマ職人になりたいらしい。

Name: Skyler Styler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She loves changing her hairstyle—tying it up, letting it down, getting it cut.
DescriptionJP: 髪を結んだり 切ったり いろんな髪型を試すのが大好き。

Name: Balen Straw
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His motto is "make hay while the sun shines, and weave baskets when it rains."
DescriptionJP: 人生 調子のいいときはガンガンいけ 悪いときはじっとしてろ がモットー。

Name: Malachi Way
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a believer in astrology, so he's always gazing at the stars.
DescriptionJP: 運命の星があることを信じていて 星の輝きを いつも気にしている。

Name: Paul Kerface
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He never shows emotion, even when something good happens.
DescriptionJP: つらいことがあっても いつも涼しい顔をして受け流している。

Name: Chip Tatum
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This player loves any kind of potato-based cuisine.
DescriptionJP: イモの料理が大好き。ジャガイモ サツマイモ サトイモ なんでも！

Name: Rebus Stumper
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This trickster is always coming up with riddles, but they're too hard, so it's no fun.
DescriptionJP: なぞなぞを作るのが大好きだけど ひねりすぎで 誰も答えられない。

Name: Cutter Shorten
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An expert at discovering cracks, he can wriggle through even the smallest gap.
DescriptionJP: 隙間を見つける天才で どんな狭い所でもすり抜ける。

Name: Manny Pickles
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He pickles everything, although it would be a good idea if he stopped pickling sweets...
DescriptionJP: 何でも干物にしてしまう。 お菓子はやめた方がいいと思うけど。

Name: Campen Allerjee
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His hobby is bell-ringing, but there's not much call for it nowadays.
DescriptionJP: 大晦日に除夜の鐘をつくのが趣味。 でも年１回しかできない。

Name: Climie Hills
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This determined lad runs up a steep hill every morning for training purposes.
DescriptionJP: 自分を鍛えるために 険しい岩山を登るのが日課。

Name: Earl Bird
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Not one to procrastinate, he does his homework months in advance.
DescriptionJP: 何でも早めに済ますタイプ。 夏休みの宿題もすぐに終わらせる。

Name: Walt Whittler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His hobby is crafting totem poles. His garden is full of them, and it's sending his mum crazy.
DescriptionJP: トーテムポールを作るのが好きで 家の庭に 何十本と立っている。

Name: Merry Piper
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He brings a smile to those around him when playing his penny whistle.
DescriptionJP: 彼が笛を吹くと なぜか周りに幸せが訪れるらしい。

Name: Traylor Beadle
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: With her gaudy accessories flailing around, she makes the dance floor her own.
DescriptionJP: 派手な羽飾りをつけて 踊るのが大好き。

Name: Doug Boateng
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: For him, nothing beats the tranquility of a fishing trip in his handcrafted dugout canoe.
DescriptionJP: カヌーを自分で作って 魚を捕りに出かけている。

Name: Fanny Oakley
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A master of the quick-draw, she rules her local laser tag.
DescriptionJP: 早撃ちの名人で ビームピストルのジュニアチャンピオン。

Name: Bucky Colt
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This rodeo champ can break any horse, no matter how wild.
DescriptionJP: 日本ロデオ大会の優勝者。 どんな馬でも見事に乗りこなす。

Name: Chuckie Roper
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Having mastered the lasso, he rarely gets up; he just ropes everything in.
DescriptionJP: 投げナワの名人で 自分の部屋にある物も すべて 投げナワを使って引き寄せる。

Name: Lucien Brightside
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He doesn't care if he doesn't get the best of everything, and he's happier for it.
DescriptionJP: 何でも最上のものを手に入れないと 気に入らない性格。

Name: Caffrey Punt
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Floating down gentle streams in his boat is this player's hobby.
DescriptionJP: 船で川下りをするのが大好き。 それも急流ではなく のんびりと。

Name: Debra Lee
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Even if it's cloudy, she'll be showing off one of her many fancy parasols.
DescriptionJP: きれいな日傘をたくさんコレクション。 天気に関係なく いつも差している。

Name: Goodie Touchouse
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He doesn't relish his reputation as a swot, but he can't go against his parents.
DescriptionJP: 優等生であることが苦痛だけど 親の期待に反抗できない。

Name: Ray Pier
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's studying fencing at the moment, and loves getting armored up for a fight.
