DescriptionJP: 西洋剣術を研究していて 鎧を着こんで対戦している。

Name: Jen Erris
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's a caring person who always takes the time to listen to her friends' problems.
DescriptionJP: 愛の伝道師として みんなの相談に積極的に乗ってくれる。

Name: Jude Ellery
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's really interested in the history of craftsmanship, especially jewelry.
DescriptionJP: 宝石の歴史を勉強していて 昔のアクセサリーに詳しい。

Name: Seamus Rock
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: It's too hard to find four-leaf clovers, so this chap is trying to cultivate them at home.
DescriptionJP: 四つ葉のクローバーの栽培に 挑戦中。

Name: Tim Roubadour
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's currently researching Italian folk songs, and has even written a few.
DescriptionJP: 幼い頃に聴いたイタリア民謡に感銘を受け 自分でも それっぽい曲を作曲している。

Name: Matt Skerade
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Greco-Roman drama is a passion for this young man, and he's trying to popularise it.
DescriptionJP: 仮面をかぶるお芝居を 日本でも流行らせようと頑張っている。

Name: Florence Tripps
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's so taken with the era of Leonardo da Vinci, he's already done a few tours of Italy.
DescriptionJP: ダ・ヴィンチが大好きで 絵の勉強にイタリアまで行ったくらい。

Name: Inke Marks
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Her clever henna tattoo designs are really going down a storm at the moment.
DescriptionJP: 彼女がデザインしたタトゥーシールは みんなに大人気。

Name: Gary Baldi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: When his teacher told him to get a haircut, he got his own back by getting a skinhead.
DescriptionJP: 先生に髪型を注意され 反発してスキンヘッドにしている。

Name: Bobby Peeler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loved playing cops and robbers when he was a boy. The problem is, he never stopped...
DescriptionJP: 任侠ものの映画に影響されて つい大股で歩いてしまう。

Name: Mark Brand
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: When he gets a good idea for a new tattoo, he scribbles it down on his body straight away.
DescriptionJP: いろんな模様を考えるのが大好きで すぐ自分の腕に描いちゃう。

Name: Hedwig Hodge
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a good heart, but he often blurts out insensitive remarks by accident.
DescriptionJP: 本当は優しいのに つい心ないことを言って 周りを傷つける。

Name: Bill Mallard
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He likes to swim. He's not very fast, but he's only doing it to relax.
DescriptionJP: のたーっと泳ぐのが大好き。 スピードは出ないけど気にしない。

Name: Roo Hopper
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She always wears clothes with big pockets, to chuck everything in. She's not very organized.
DescriptionJP: お腹にポケットのついた服を着ていて なんでもその中に放り込む。

Name: Cole Bear
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He looks quiet, but he's famous for having very powerful hands.
DescriptionJP: 一見おっとりした姿だけど 指でモノをつかむ力は凄まじい。

Name: Al Opino
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves any kind of spicy Asian cuisine, so he's always getting takeout.
DescriptionJP: アジアの辛い料理を食べ歩くのが 大好き。

Name: Oz Tier
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: There's nothing wrong with a firm bed, but this guy sleeps on the floor.
DescriptionJP: ベッドは硬い方がいいと信じているらしく ついに 石の上で眠るようになったという。

Name: Shelley Wordsworth
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This poetic soul recites his poems whenever the spirit moves him—even on the bus.
DescriptionJP: ひらめくと 場所に関係なく 朗読しちゃう 自称詩人。

Name: Stu Potter
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He relishes rich piping-hot stews, and eats them all year round.
DescriptionJP: 鍋料理が大好きで 真夏でも フーフー言いながら 食べている。

Name: Bern Ballast
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's trying to lose enough weight to be an effective hang-glider pilot.
DescriptionJP: 体を軽くすれば空を飛べると信じていて 無理なダイエットをしている。

Name: Heidi Rood
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Inspired by fairytales, she goes about in a red hooded cloak, carrying a basket.
DescriptionJP: いつも フードつきの赤いコートを着て かわいいバスケットを 持ち歩いている。

Name: Elvis Schumacher
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His grandfather was a legendary cobbler, and he's inherited his skills.
DescriptionJP: おじいさんの手伝いをしているうちに 靴作りの名人になった。

Name: Snezhana White
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She likes apples so much that she once ate a rotten one by mistake.
DescriptionJP: 傷んだリンゴを うっかり食べてしまい 大変な目にあったという過去を持つ。

Name: Abel Forager
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He hunts and gathers food on the moors, then makes delicious meals with what he finds.
DescriptionJP: 山菜を採りに行って 自分で料理するのが趣味。

Name: Will Wary
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a doubting heart, and doesn't take anyone at their word. It's quite grating.
DescriptionJP: 人の言うことを絶対に信じない。 先生の授業ですらも！

Name: Rocco Shale
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's on a quest to collect rocks from all the hills and dales across the country.
DescriptionJP: 石の塊を探すのが趣味で 全国の野山を巡っている。

Name: Bob Jobbe
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's head of the local "good deed a day" club. What a nice young man.
DescriptionJP: １日１回人助けをする 『人助け協会』会長。

Name: Lee Bei
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He lost his father when he was young, so he's taken on a lot of responsibilities.
DescriptionJP: 父親を早くに亡くしたので 自分が家族を支えると誓った。

Name: Quincy Wang
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's thinking of writing a commentary on Sun Tzu's "Art of War."
DescriptionJP: 孫子の兵法を研究していて 自分で本を書いたくらい。

Name: Dan Fei
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Once he gets his blood up, nothing can stop him. It can be quite problematic.
DescriptionJP: 暴れ出すと手がつけられない。 橋を通せんぼして大騒ぎしたことも。

Name: Liddy Gan
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She will probably be popular with the boys when she's a bit older.
DescriptionJP: 中学生なのに すごい色気で 大人までもがフラフラに。

Name: Tom Bulldown
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He lives in an old historic building, but he'd rather have something with more mod cons.
DescriptionJP: 築１００年以上の古い家に住んでいるため 現代的なマンションに強い憧れを持つ。

Name: Ria Vivalist
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She wants to find a group of people who share her love of Chinese poetry.
DescriptionJP: 『詩吟』の魅力に取りつかれてしまい 同好会をつくる計画を立てているらしい。

Name: Sunniffa Scentgood
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She has the ability to identify distinct locations by the smell of the wind.
DescriptionJP: 風の匂いが瞬時に嗅ぎ分けられるという 使いどころの難しい 変な特技の持ち主。

Name: Julia Mason
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Creating neat objets d'art from stone is this girl's main hobby.
DescriptionJP: 大きな石を コツコツと削り続けては 様々なオブジェを作り出している彫刻家。

Name: Ria Carnival
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She goes to Rio every year to show off her samba dancing skills.
DescriptionJP: サンバダンスの名人。 毎年リオに踊りに行くほど。

Name: Gracey Grapples
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Don't underestimate her ability in Brazilian jiu-jitsu. If you do, she'll break your arm.
DescriptionJP: ブラジリアン柔術の達人。 舐めてかかると腕を折られちゃうぞ。

Name: Shep Woolacombe
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His placid demeanor makes him an easy target for bullies.
DescriptionJP: 子ヒツジのように おとなしい性格のため 不良の標的にされることが何かと多い。

Name: Sue Accharin
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Her motto is "Smile and the world smiles with you!"
DescriptionJP: 『明るく振る舞っていればみんな幸せ』 というモットーで 今日も笑顔を振りまく。

Name: Venus Demila
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She loves big statues, so she has a huge collection of photographs of them.
DescriptionJP: 巨大な像に目がなく 写真を撮ってコレクションにしている。

Name: Steven Nevets
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: For some reason, he's obsessed with digging holes on flat ground.
DescriptionJP: 平らな地面を見かけると なぜか途端に 穴を掘りたくてたまらなくなるという。

Name: Gerald Gerund
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's making an advanced study of grammar at the moment.
DescriptionJP: 新旧問わず日本語のありとあらゆる文章を 日々 研究しているという熱心な勉強家。

Name: Tracy Tracker
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Sometimes she gets herself lost following interesting animals around.
DescriptionJP: 動物を見かけると すぐ追いかけてしまって 気づくと迷子に。

Name: Bernadette Stoker
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She gets annoyed at anyone who shows up late—except herself.
DescriptionJP: 時間にルーズなクセに他人が遅刻をすると フキゲンになってしまう困ったちゃん。

Name: Keshia Readingplace
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's popular down at the library, because she hands out home-made bookmarks.
DescriptionJP: 趣味で作った栞を 図書館で配ったところ 大人気となり 今もリクエストが絶えない。

Name: Sahara Kalahari
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She always fancied living in a desert, so she filled her garden full of sand.
DescriptionJP: 砂漠での生活に憧れていて 自宅の庭を全部砂場にした。

Name: Fala Polaris
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has the useful knack of navigating by looking at the night sky.
DescriptionJP: 星を見ながら 正しい方角を 旅することができる。

Name: Ian Flappable
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Whatever the crisis, he reads the opposition's game flawlessly.
DescriptionJP: どんなに不利な状況に置かれたとしても 静かに相手の動きを観察して対応する。

Name: Penny Linguine
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: They say that the fresh pasta she makes is even better than her dad's.
DescriptionJP: お父さんよりも うどんの麺を作るのが うまいらしい。

Name: Poppy Playhard
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She does her homework before she goes to school, so she's free after class.
DescriptionJP: 早朝から勉強しているので 放課後は自由に遊んでいる。

Name: Connie Fuchsia
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's interested in Eastern philosophy, so she's always reading about it.
DescriptionJP: 歴史上の人物である 『荘子』のような 生き方に憧れて 本を何度も読んでいる。

Name: Baron Blackgold
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His dream is to strike oil and become a wealthy oil magnate.
DescriptionJP: 日本のどこかで油田を掘り当てて 油田王になるという 野望を持っている。

Name: Marty Oshker
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Underneath the many layers she wears to keep warm, she's surprisingly tiny.
DescriptionJP: 服を何枚も着こんでいるので 見た目よりもはるかに小柄。

Name: Nat Meg
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's an expert at fooling his opponents with feints. They fall for it every time.
DescriptionJP: 相手のウラをかく天才。 彼の作戦は誰にも予想できない。

Name: Eddy Steady
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He stands tall like a mountain in the face of any charge.
DescriptionJP: 激しいブロックや スライディングにも 岩山のようにどっしりと構えて突き進む。

Name: Severin Volei
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's a champion racquetball player, but she worries about the shallow talent pool.
DescriptionJP: ラケットボールの中学チャンピオン。 競技人口を増やすための活動をしている。

Name: Brava Hardy
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She can watch scary horror films all by herself, she's so brave.
DescriptionJP: みんなが怖がるホラー映画を １人で平気で見ている。

Name: Helmut Hoarder
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He collects antique helmets, especially ones that have funny shapes.
DescriptionJP: 古い兜を集めていて 特に角のついたものがお気に入り。

Name: Strama daKoto
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She learnt to play the guqin when she lived in China as an infant.
DescriptionJP: 子どものころ中国に住んでいて 珍しい琴を弾くことができる。

Name: Olaf Nobeard
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He longs to craft a boat from wood, so he's reading up about it now.
DescriptionJP: 木造船を造ることに憧れて 毎日 本を読んでいる。

Name: Gudrun Lodestone
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's such a confident maritime navigator that she needn't rely on her GPS.
DescriptionJP: 航海術を研究していて ＧＰＳがなくても航路を設定できる。

Name: Carol Fairfoot
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She dreams of dancing at a medieval-style ball, so she practices in period costumes.
DescriptionJP: 中世の優雅な舞踏会に憧れて 自宅でドレスを着て 踊りの練習をしている。

Name: Michael Shako
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Napoleonic helmets are pretty rare these days, so he collects them for posterity.
DescriptionJP: 海外で使われている円筒形の帽子を 部屋いっぱいにコレクションしている。

Name: Direm Ederi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He likes to trot around with no destination in mind, like a chilled-out camel.
DescriptionJP: ラクダのようにのんびりと 散歩するのが大好き。

Name: Marina Coaster
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She has an abiding fascination with channels and seaways around the world—especially the Tsugaru Strait.
DescriptionJP: 各地の海峡を見るのが好きな 海峡マニア。 中でもやはり 津軽海峡は格別なのだとか。

Name: Wowzer Bigtop
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has peerless skill in ball-balancing acrobatic routines!
DescriptionJP: 玉乗りの曲芸をやらせたら 天下一品！

Name: Derry Farmer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Every morning, he goes to the barn to milk his cow by hand.
DescriptionJP: 毎朝 飼っている乳牛の 乳しぼりをやっている。

Name: Devlin Ogor
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He used to be handsome, but his face warped as the result of a curse, they say.
DescriptionJP: 絶世の美少年だったが 呪いでこんな顔になったらしい。

Name: Fez Monkton
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He longs for the azure skies of the Moroccan desert, and he loves Bedouin dress.
DescriptionJP: モロッコの文化に憧れて いつも民族衣装を着ている。

Name: Berthel Stagg
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's an ardent breeder of stag beetles, so in the summer they take over the house.
DescriptionJP: クワガタの養殖をやっていて 夏には部屋がクワガタだらけに。

Name: Damon Sumner
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He likes to summon foul beasts from the netherworld, to help him out during matches.
DescriptionJP: 魔物を呼び出して その力でサッカーが うまくなるよう研究中。

Name: Anders Thettock
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Aiming for the dental profession, he hopes to pioneer pain-free forms of treatment.
DescriptionJP: 絶対に痛くない治療をする 歯科医を目指している。

Name: Laititia Cheeseman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She produces delicious dairy-based foods with fresh milk.
DescriptionJP: 新鮮なミルクを使って 乳製品を作るのが大好き。

Name: Isodoura Bouquet
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She plans to be an aromatherapist, so she always carries around phials of scent.
DescriptionJP: アロマセラピーを勉強していて いつもアロマオイルを持ち歩いている。

Name: May Jarrett
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Baton twirling is the hobby of this youngster. She hasn't dropped it while performing yet!
DescriptionJP: 中学バトントワリングの世界では有名人。 華麗なバトンさばきで 見る者を虜にする。

Name: Des Einer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: It's said that if you get him to design your business card, you're sure to do well.
DescriptionJP: 名刺デザインの神童。 その名刺を使うと 商売がうまくいくとか。

Name: Kev Fiyah
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He mitigates the risk of sunstroke by wearing a stylish keffiyeh.
DescriptionJP: 日よけに いつもターバンを かぶっている。

Name: Shadi Mesmer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's been studying hypnotism, but so far, he's only managed to hypnotize himself.
DescriptionJP: 催眠術を研究しているが なぜか自分にばかり かかってしまう。

Name: Preston Digitator
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's got a keen interest in traditional magic tricks and sleight of hand techniques.
DescriptionJP: 日本伝統の手品である『和妻』を 研究している。

Name: Roman Fawkes
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's mad about fireworks, so he travels round the country to watch different displays.
DescriptionJP: 花火大会を見るのが大好きで 日本中を回っている。

Name: Morty Portland
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves concrete, and wants to make the world as wild about it as he is.
DescriptionJP: コンクリートが大好きで 温かみのあるものにできないか研究している。

Name: Fabrice Pesci
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's working hard to produce the best factory-farmed tuna possible.
DescriptionJP: 天然モノにも負けないような マグロの養殖を目指して奮闘中。

Name: Boo Spector
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd like to build the ultimate haunted house one day.
DescriptionJP: 誰もが怖がる 究極のお化け屋敷を 作ろうとしている。

Name: Cole Tivator
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's trying to reclaim some wasteground, and aims to turn it into productive farmland.
DescriptionJP: 荒れ地を畑として耕すことに 一生懸命になっている。

Name: Blagun White
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His hobby is collecting old-fashioned monochrome postcards.
DescriptionJP: 昔のモノクロの絵はがきを コレクションするのが趣味。

Name: Jeanie Tanner
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's well versed in North African cuisine, and can make a great spicy stew.
DescriptionJP: 北アフリカ名物のタジン鍋を 作ることができる。

Name: Monty Tasker
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He swears blind that he can't think straight without the background noise of the radio.
DescriptionJP: ラジオを聴きながらでないと 勉強ができない『ながら族』。

Name: Artie Xan
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a gourmand who insists on handmade bread, eschewing supermarket loaves.
DescriptionJP: 臼と杵でついた餅しか 絶対に食べようとしない。

Name: Genghis Cohen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He dreams of riding through the Mongolian steppe on horseback.
DescriptionJP: 馬でモンゴルの平原を 旅するのが夢。

Name: Adam Venturus
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's an adventurous eater who loves to eat kangaroo and crocodile.
DescriptionJP: ワニとかカンガルーとか 珍しい肉を食べるのが大好き。

Name: Zahida Zahid
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Whenever she goes out, she's always very careful to keep her face covered.
DescriptionJP: 外出時には すっぽりと顔を覆う服を いつも着ている。

Name: Zowie Trope
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a collector of old-fashioned magic lanterns. He'll show his slides if you ask.
DescriptionJP: 懐かしい幻灯機を集めていて 時々上映会をやっている。

Name: Roland Lex
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a collector of rare watches, with examples from all over the world.
DescriptionJP: めずらしい腕時計を集めているコレクター。 彼のもとには 海外からの取材が来るほど。

Name: Holly Marx
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's a talented designer of greetings cards, so she's extra busy at Christmas.
DescriptionJP: グリーティングカードのデザイン名人。 クリスマス前は大忙し。

Name: Springer Boreham
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's really got the knack of sinking wells. He hits the jackpot even in the most arid terrain.
DescriptionJP: 井戸を掘る名人。 どんな枯れた土地でも 見事に掘り当てる。

Name: Kandhul Lai
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's not a fan of electric light, so he uses paper lanterns instead.
DescriptionJP: 電灯ではなく行灯で生活しているという 今時珍しい人。

Name: Kit Fischer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's convinced that catfish can avert catastrophes, so he keeps a pond of them.
DescriptionJP: 地震とナマズの関係を研究していて 家の水槽はナマズだらけ。

Name: Becks Binder
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's pretty handy at restoring old books to good condition.
DescriptionJP: 破損した本は どんな古いものでも 見事に修理してしまう。

Name: Ralph Chasing
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His ardent curiosity towards the spirit world is given vent in excursions to "haunted" sites.
DescriptionJP: 本物の妖怪を求めて 全国を旅行中。

Name: Phil Debonair
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: If you need a fish filleting, bring it to this guy! He'll have it deboned in no time.
DescriptionJP: 魚をおろす名人。 小魚からマグロの解体まで 何でもござれ！

Name: Si Sosman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has his own blend of soy sauce, which tastes great even on chips.
DescriptionJP: 彼が作るラー油は どんな料理にも合うと 大評判となり 町内でブームが起きている。

Name: Aaron Gossamer
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's rather self-conscious about his appearance and mannerisms.
DescriptionJP: 常に自分の行動が 美しく優雅でなければ 気が済まないという たいへんなナルシスト。

Name: Pomponius Fanfair
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves the idea of royal pageants, often daydreaming that he's in the seat of honor.
DescriptionJP: 大名行列に憧れていて 自分が運ばれることを夢見ている。

Name: Fanella Waftgood
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She collects ornamental fans, and loves finding rare or interesting ones.
DescriptionJP: 羽子板のコレクター。 羽子板市のときには 必ず浅草に来る。

Name: Irina Swift
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's an expert at ironing, and she can do a shirt in one minute.
DescriptionJP: どんなシャツでも １分でアイロンがけしてしまう。

Name: Rick Shaw
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's building up his strength by offering rides in his hand-pulled cart.
DescriptionJP: 人力車を引き お客さんを乗せている。 市内の観光案内もお手のものである。

Name: Montaine Skalin
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He climbs up Mount Fuji once a year when the season comes round.
DescriptionJP: とにかく登山が大好きで 年に一度は 富士山の頂上まで登らないと気が済まない。

Name: Meowlinda Purrsival
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: There's a persistent rumor that bad things happen to those whose path she crosses.
DescriptionJP: 彼女が横切ると その人に不幸が 訪れるという もっぱらのウワサ。

Name: Rune Sigilsson
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's always doodling strange geometric patterns in the playground.
DescriptionJP: 学校のグラウンドに いつも訳の分からない模様を描いている。

Name: Onslow Mastick
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He takes a scholarly interest in the origin of surnames.
DescriptionJP: 名字の由来に詳しく クラスメートの祖先をピタリと言い当てる。

Name: Blowie Armstraw
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A skilled grass trumpeter, he can play any tune on a single blade of grass.
DescriptionJP: 笹笛の名人。 １枚の笹の葉で あらゆる曲を吹ける。

Name: Paddy Filler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's trying to develop a strain of rice that will grow in any soil.
DescriptionJP: どんな土地でも育つ稲を研究して 毎日 田んぼにいる。

Name: Avid Peddler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wants to be a professional cyclist, so he cycles 100km every day as training.
DescriptionJP: 競輪選手を目指して 毎日１００キロも自転車で走っている。

Name: Woody Prince
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves old Japanese woodblock prints, and dreams of making his own one day.
DescriptionJP: 中学生なのに 浮世絵に魅せられて 自分でも作ろうとしている。

Name: Demerara Kane
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves sugar cane, and he even chews it when he's at school.
DescriptionJP: サトウキビが大好きで 学校の中でも いつもかじっている。

Name: Tiny Jetson
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's got a strange and very specific passion for miniature jet engines.
DescriptionJP: ジェット機の中でも 小型のものだけが 好きな ちょっと変わったマニア。

Name: Joe Java
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's setting up a greenhouse in his garden so he can grow his own coffee.
DescriptionJP: 本格的なコーヒー栽培を目指して 自宅にハウスを作っている。

Name: Wulf Blackbean
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves the bean-based cuisines of Brazil, but his friends don't share his passion.
DescriptionJP: ブラジルの豆料理が大好き。 でも友人は なかなか食べてくれない。

Name: Neville Boyle
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's got some very particular ideas about the best way to prepare rice.
DescriptionJP: おいしいご飯を炊くには かまどが一番と こだわっている。

Name: Ameen Abel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's an easy-going guy who easily forgives those who inconvenience him.
DescriptionJP: 彼に迷惑をかけても「いいのや」と 気持ちよく許してくれる。

Name: Bombasta Flamboyanzi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's always in trouble with the teacher for her gaudy, carnivalesque outfits.
DescriptionJP: カーニバルのような 派手な衣装で いつも先生に怒られている。

Name: Fada Prendi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Loves designer Italian brands. Her schoolbag is always high fashion.
DescriptionJP: イタリアのブランド品が大好きで 学校用のカバンも イタリア製のものを使う。

Name: Bella Baker
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Loves baking bread. People wonder what will emerge from her oven next.
DescriptionJP: 自分で考えた創作パンを作るのが趣味。 彼女の新作パンに期待している友達は多い。

Name: Olivia Palme
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She specializes in making dishes with palm oil. She's pretty generous with the portions, too.
DescriptionJP: パーム油を使った料理が得意で みんなに振る舞っている。

Name: Gustav Weathervane
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He can read the wind, and uses it to control the ball's movements.
DescriptionJP: フィールドを吹き抜ける風の動きを読んで ボールをコントロールできる 風の使い手。

Name: Grover Noggin
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He looks as if he's staring into space, but he's watching like a hawk.
DescriptionJP: 何も考えていないように見られがちだが 本人いわく 常に鋭く観察しているという。

Name: Blazer Firefoot
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He can blast the ball through the opposition's defence like a pillar of flame.
DescriptionJP: まるで火柱のように どんなボールも激しいキックで蹴り返す。

Name: Adam Montayne
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He uses his size and bulk to maintain possession of the ball as he surges forward.
DescriptionJP: 大きな体で 確実にボールをキープしながら 走り込む。

Name: Chauncey Slinka
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Her preferred tactic is sneaking up on the enemy goal from an unexpected angle.
DescriptionJP: 予想外の方向から 唐突に走り込んでいき 敵のゴールを容赦なく狙うプレイスタイル。

Name: Leighton Bolt
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He can get to the ball in a flash, like lightning in the heavens.
DescriptionJP: まるで天の稲妻のように 彼の手はボールに届く。

Name: Lucien Thrope
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's frightened of silver bullets, but there aren't that many around here!
DescriptionJP: なぜか銀の弾丸を恐れているが 日本では 普通見かけない。

Name: Lenton Gouger
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His pumpkin carving skills are legendary, and he's much in demand at Halloween time.
DescriptionJP: かぼちゃをくり抜いて ランタンを作る名人。

Name: Titania Khamun
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She doesn't like going out if she isn't well wrapped up...
DescriptionJP: 包帯を巻いていないと なぜか安心できないらしい。

Name: Eveline Veitch
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She practises flying on a broomstick, but she hasn't had much success so far.
DescriptionJP: ほうきに乗って空を飛べると信じて 特訓しているが もちろん飛べない。

Name: Eldritch Priest
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a collection of ancient ritual objects. Spooky stuff.
DescriptionJP: 昔の怪しげな儀式に使われたアイテムを 色々集めている。

Name: Gene Bulge
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's looking for a slimline wallet that won't spoil the line of his trousers.
DescriptionJP: ポケットが財布で膨れるのがイヤで 薄い財布を探している。

Name: Candy Reviva
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's trying to pioneer an updated line of traditional confectionery.
DescriptionJP: 和菓子に魅せられ 新しい和菓子を研究中。

Name: Pacey Mack
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: If you need something doing to your computer, then she's the one to ask.
DescriptionJP: コンピューターのオぺレーションを やらせたら 彼女に敵う者はいない。

Name: Anil Latikal
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's working on a grand scheme to mathematically assess human ability.
DescriptionJP: 人間の能力を数字で測ろうと 日夜研究している。

Name: Indy Ferrante
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: For someone who claims to be logical, he flies into a temper easily.
DescriptionJP: 自分は論理的で感情などないと言うくせに 白黒つかないことがあると すぐ怒りだす。

Name: Stan Tistischen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's adept at assembling statistical data, and then analyzing it.
DescriptionJP: 統計データを集めて 解析するのが得意。

Name: Simon Borg
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A robotics genius, his dream is to build a robot which is beyond human.
DescriptionJP: ロボット工学の天才で 人間を超えるロボットを作るつもり。

Name: Clark Phylen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's great at organizing data, but once he's organized it, he doesn't do anything with it.
DescriptionJP: 情報整理のプロだが 整理するだけで 宝の持ち腐れ。

Name: Gram Vineela
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves old gramophones and even records new discs for them.
DescriptionJP: 蓄音機の音に感動してからというもの アナログレコードを自作しているという。

Name: Yasser Rightaway
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Even if he's really wound up and angry, he still does exactly what he's told.
DescriptionJP: どんなに怒っていても お願いされると つい 素直に従ってしまう。

Name: Adora Shivers
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She's interested in ghost stories and spooky films, but she's still level-headed.
DescriptionJP: とある離れ小島にある神社の娘なので 父親の手伝いで 巫女さんをやっていた。

Name: Roland Allardyce
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves playing backgammon, but none of his friends at school will play it with him.
DescriptionJP: すごろくが大好きなんだけど 同級生は 誰も遊んでくれない。

Name: Lacy Cagney
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She hopes to become a tough detective one day, but she'll have to get some nous first.
DescriptionJP: かっこいい刑事に憧れて特訓中。 だけど動きが遅いんだ。

Name: Justice Gavel
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She dreams of being a high court judge, so she studies really hard at school.
DescriptionJP: 正義の裁判官を目指して 今から猛勉強中。

Name: Raleigh Greenstreet
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He dreams of winning a race in a fully solar-powered car someday.
DescriptionJP: 仲間たちと作り上げたソーラーカーで レースに出場して優勝するのが目標。

Name: Melody Toontune
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She hopes for success as a singer, singing theme tunes for cartoons.
DescriptionJP: アニメ番組の主題歌を歌って アイドルになるのが夢。

Name: Zip Windrush
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Swift as the wind, no one can follow this lightning player.
DescriptionJP: 風のような疾さでフィールドを駆け巡る。 彼の動きについていくのは至難の業だ。

Name: Buster Lungs
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An expert in free diving, he can hold his breath for five minutes at a time.
DescriptionJP: 素潜りの達人。 ５分以上 水の中に潜っていられる。

Name: Stanza Verse
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Her hobby is reading poetry. She records her own writings in a handmade pad she carries.
DescriptionJP: 俳句を詠むのが趣味。 いつも筆と短冊を持ち歩いている。

Name: Dextra Gleeson
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She loves American TV shows so much that she even subscribes to American streaming services.
DescriptionJP: 海外ドラマが大好きで 国外の動画配信サービスも使っているほど。

Name: Aidull Wanabi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This one dreams of success and fame, and he's none too fussed how he achieves it.
DescriptionJP: 上昇志向で 将来なんでもいいから ビッグになってやると思っている。

Name: Earle Humble
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He was born to an aristocratic family, but he longs to be amongst everyday folk.
DescriptionJP: 高貴な家の生まれだが その生活に疲れ 癒やしを求める。

Name: Rich Fowler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's aggressive. He has certainly gone a bit too far on occasion.
DescriptionJP: アグレッシブだが ちょっとアブない行動をとることも。

Name: Rio Shoring
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a soothing personality, and always helps his friends resolve their woes.
DescriptionJP: 安心させる達人。 相談した人は その夜からぐっすり眠れる。

Name: Joy Seeker
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She always ponders to herself: "what is the good life?"
DescriptionJP: 幸福な生活とは何かを いつも考えている。

Name: Haydn Woe
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He carries around a great sadness within him, but no one realizes.
DescriptionJP: いつも悲しみを心に秘めているが 誰も気づいていない。

Name: Levi Atherton
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has an uncanny ability to calm the waves with his mere presence.
DescriptionJP: 彼が海に行くと 波が静まるという 不思議な力を持っている。

Name: Flick Screening
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She runs a small cinema club so that she can introduce people to hidden classics.
DescriptionJP: 隠れた名作映画をみんなに見てもらうため ミニシアターを運営したいと考えている。

Name: Buff Bagenal
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: If some fancy new bag comes out, he has to have it, whether he needs it or not.
DescriptionJP: 必要ないのに 新しいカバンが出たら つい欲しくなって 買ってしまう。

Name: Mariah Knowles
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An aspiring singer whose ambition crosses borders, nay continents!
DescriptionJP: 日本だけなんて狭すぎる。 目指すは アジアのトップアイドル！

Name: Phil Harmonic
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He wants to become an orchestral conductor, so he stands in front of a mirror, waving a baton.
DescriptionJP: 将来 オーケストラの指揮者になるために 自分の部屋でタクトを振って特訓している。

Name: Ghoulian Haunter
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His ghostly, floating walk freaks people out. Some say they've seen him go through walls!
DescriptionJP: いつも ふわふわと漂うように 歩いている。

Name: Jacko Lenton
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: This prankster loves scaring people with his spooky pumpkin mask.
DescriptionJP: かぼちゃのお面で 人を驚かせる事が 好きだという イタズラっ子。

Name: Dee Tarrant
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a classical realist who believes that peace is preserved only by might.
DescriptionJP: 力こそ すべての平和をもたらすと 信じている。

Name: Lee Bartarian
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a liberal, and he often asserts that school regulations ought to be relaxed.
DescriptionJP: 自由を殊更重視して 校則も廃止しようと主張している。

Name: Amir Rika
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A staunch follower of the American dream, he hopes to amass a vast fortune one day.
DescriptionJP: 中学を卒業したら 単身アメリカに渡って 大金持ちになるという夢を持っている。

Name: Ewan Envoi
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd like to make friends around the world and forge international links.
DescriptionJP: 世界中のいろんな人達と 仲良くしたいと思っている。

Name: Jen DeRites
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She believes that people can connect through dance, using it to communicate with people around the world.
DescriptionJP: 「踊りで人は通じ合える」と言い 世界中の人と ダンスで意思疎通をしている。

Name: Judge Jury
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a strong sense of right and wrong, but he struggles to take others' opinions on board.
DescriptionJP: 正義を重視するのはいいが ちょっと人の話を聞かない傾向も。

Name: Leo Maine
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He had a hard time when he was a kid, but he battled through, and he's stronger for it.
DescriptionJP: 子どものころ谷に落ちたが 這い上がってきた ガッツの持ち主。

Name: Scorpia Venin
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Her tongue is so sharp it can pierce the hearts of her foes like a needle.
DescriptionJP: こう見えても 実はかなりの毒舌家。 相手の心に針を刺すこともしばしば…。

Name: Noel Taurius
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: They call him the Crazy Bull. He's seen off many would-be matadors.
DescriptionJP: 暴れ牛の異名をとる。 彼に吹き飛ばされた人 多数。

Name: Pan Kidd
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A peaceful guy who likes to spend his days snoozing in the meadow.

Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: An altruistic fellow who wants to help during a crisis. He's on a crisis-searching tour now.
DescriptionJP: 世界の危機を救うために 危機を探して旅している。

Name: Galahad Chevalier
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a chivalrous person who always looks to help others above all else.
DescriptionJP: 人助けを何よりも重んじる 騎士道精神の持ち主。

Name: Wanda Spelling
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: She possesses magic powers which she uses to help others.
DescriptionJP: 不思議なおまじないで みんなを助けてくれる。

Name: Nick Pincher
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has the uncanny ability to read the contents of a person's pockets in an instant.
DescriptionJP: 相手が何を持っているのか たちどころに見破ってしまう。

Name: Marshall Artison
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'll take on any opponent with nothing other than his fists.
DescriptionJP: どんなに強い相手に対しても ２つのこぶしだけで 立ち向かう。

Name: Mary Curey
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: People are cured of all ailments just by being near her. Provided they don't stay too long...
DescriptionJP: 彼女が手をかざすだけで なぜか みんな元気を取り戻す。

Name: Ian Bick
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's still young, but he has a keen sensitivity for poetry and has produced a slim volume.
DescriptionJP: 若いながらも 和歌を研究して 本まで書いているほど。

Name: Jib Spinaker
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's already a champion yacht racer, and he's hoping to compete internationally.
DescriptionJP: ヨットレースの日本ジュニアチャンピオン。 目指すは世界！

Name: Odo Riffeck
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He practices incense appreciation but is often mistaken for doing aromatherapy.
DescriptionJP: 香りを楽しむ香道を嗜んでいるが アロマとよく勘違いされる。

Name: Fox Wiley
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He revels in outfoxing opponents with tricks. But deep down, he just wants to be friends.
DescriptionJP: 相手の裏をかくのが生きがい。 でも 悪意はないんだ。

Name: Gladius Swinger
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's fascinated by Roman gladiators, so he's always waving a toy sword around.
DescriptionJP: ローマ時代の剣闘士に憧れて おもちゃの剣を振り回している。

Name: Asif Ecks
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's really into special effects, and he hopes to work in Hollywood one day.
DescriptionJP: ＳＦＸの達人になって いつかアメリカで活躍したいと思っている。

Name: Roy Ellway
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd like to be in control of the rail company so that he can run lines to his favoured spots.
DescriptionJP: 鉄道会社を作って 好きな場所に電車を走らせたい。

Name: Scott Amundsen
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd love to go on a polar expedition, so he's trying to join an expedition team.
DescriptionJP: 南極探検に憧れていて 探検隊に加わりたいらしい。

Name: Mike Roscopy
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves investigating the world of tiny things with his microscope.
DescriptionJP: 顕微鏡でミクロの世界を覗くのが 大好き。

Name: Gruff Dorman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He'd like to be the concierge of a first-rate hotel some day.
DescriptionJP: 一流ホテルの コンシェルジュになるのが夢。

Name: Snowy Bergman
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: When winter comes, he goes up north to view the ice floes.
DescriptionJP: 冬になったら 必ず北海道に 流氷を見に行く。

Name: Tiger Bleriot
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's got a thing for old biplanes, and he's got his heart set on a ride in one.
DescriptionJP: 複葉機が大好きで いずれ 自分で飛ばしたいと思っている。

Name: Ugg LeMugg
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He swears blind that his appearance is the result of a cruel joke.
DescriptionJP: 天狗に出会って からかわれたことがあると 本人は言い張っている。

Name: Hans Popov
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has this recurring dream that his hands fall off, so he checks them when he awakes.
DescriptionJP: 腕を切られる夢を 毎晩のように見るので 朝必ず確認する。

Name: Norman Zeus
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He only needs to look at a glass of wine to start feeling sleepy.
DescriptionJP: お酒を見ると 飲むわけでもないのに なぜか 眠ってしまう。

Name: Tommo Marrow
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's got a bizarre aversion to dogs, monkeys, pheasants and peaches.
DescriptionJP: なぜか 犬とサルとキジが大の苦手。 あと モモも嫌い。

Name: Lyle Covet
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He dreams of amassing a hoard of treasure on an island somewhere.
DescriptionJP: 自分の島に 全国の宝物を集めたいと思っている。

Name: Graham Dupree
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He can remember every racing result for the last ten years.
DescriptionJP: レースのことなら １０年前の結果も 全部覚えている。

Name: Dirk Byker
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's going to try his hand at motocross racing, just as soon as he gets his licence.
DescriptionJP: バイクのモトクロスレースが大好きで 免許を取ったら 挑戦したい。

Name: Charles LeMans
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a strong contender in long-distance endurance races.
DescriptionJP: ひたすら走る耐久レースに とても強い。

Name: Walter Carr
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: His ambition is to drive across the wilds of Africa someday.
DescriptionJP: アフリカの荒野を 車で走り抜けたいと 夢見ている。

Name: Buzz Scrambler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's really into supercross racing. That's the one with all the funny obstacles.
DescriptionJP: スーパークロスと呼ばれるバイクレースが 大好き。

Name: Nifty Throttler
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He plans to distinguish himself nationally in bike racing competitions.
DescriptionJP: オートバイのレースで 全日本チャンピオンになるのが夢。

Name: Dino Zolletta
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's always drinking cappuccinos. He also seems like a bit of a poser.
NameJP: ディノ・マルディーニ
DescriptionJP: カプチーノが大好き。 でも飲んでいる姿は ちょっと背伸びしすぎ。

Name: Decker Pile
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a meticulous person. They say he's searching for his missing twin brother.
DescriptionJP: いつでもどこでも用意周到！ 双子の弟を捜しているらしい。

Name: Chucky Cardaway
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: Apparently, this intimidating player is searching for his long-lost twin.
DescriptionJP: 人は彼を死神と恐れる。 双子の兄を捜しているらしい。

Name: Bernie Ellement
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves the color red, because it matches the burning passion in his heart!
DescriptionJP: 赤色が大好き。 燃えるハートの熱血ボーイ！

Name: Woody Ellement
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: There's a perplexing and enigmatic aura around this player and his illusory tactics.
DescriptionJP: 摩訶不思議な雰囲気。 変幻自在なトリックプレイが特徴！

Name: Gail Ellement
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He believes in the simple life. But on the pitch, he'll be up in your business in no time.
DescriptionJP: お気楽極楽がモットー。 すばやい動きで相手を翻弄！

Name: Clay Ellement
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's always calm and collected, and is respected for an intelligent style of football.
DescriptionJP: いつも沈着冷静。 自他共に認める頭脳派プレイヤー。

Name: Neville Goodenough
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's determined to stand out from the crowd, and he'll spend money to do it if necessary.
DescriptionJP: 注目を集めるのが天才的！！ そのための出費は惜しまない。

Name: Lucien Rarey
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He has a sparkling presence, causing many people to take great pains to seek him out.
DescriptionJP: きらりと輝く存在感の持ち主。 見かけるといいことあるかも！？

Name: Stackem Skyhigh
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's a larger than life guy who demonstrates a sincere passion.
DescriptionJP: １人で２枚の存在感。 心はいつでもバーニング中！

Name: Anfaira D'vantage
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He loves Japanese games and anime. He's always bulk purchasing trading cards.
DescriptionJP: 日本のゲームやアニメが大好き。 カードはいつも景気よく大人買い。

Name: Walken Ruhlbuch
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: He's an expert on all trading card related matters.
DescriptionJP: カードゲームのことなら何でもお任せ。 なぜならば彼は チェアマンなのだから…。

Name: Maasa Sudou
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A member of a popular girl band. She might look sweet, but she hates to lose.
DescriptionJP: 人気アイドルグループのメンバー。 こう見えて負けず嫌いなの♪

Name: Yurina Kumai
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A member of a popular girl band. She's rather self-conscious about her height.
DescriptionJP: 人気アイドルグループのメンバー。 背が高いのが悩みのタネ…♪

Name: Miyabi Natsuyaki
Game: Inazuma Eleven 3: Lightning Bolt / Bomb Blast / Team Ogre Attacks!
Description: A member of a popular girl band. She's a little bit shy.
DescriptionJP: 人気アイドルグループのメンバー。 ちょっと人見知りかも…♪

Name: Arion Sherwind
Description: An innocent young boy who adores football. A player as pleasant as a breath of fresh air.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 天真爛漫なサッカー大好き少年。 そよ風のような 爽やかさを持つ。

Name: Victor Blade
Description: A dark side striker whose incredible talents overwhelm all who witness them.
Team2JP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: ずば抜けた才能で周りを圧倒する ダークサイドストライカー。

Name: Riccardo Di Rigo
Description: He guides his team so precisely it's as if he were conducting an orchestra. A genius playmaker known as the "Virtuoso" by many.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: まるで指揮者のように 的確な指示を出す その指揮ぶりは神のタクトと呼ばれる。

Name: Jean-Pierre Lapin
Description: He's not the biggest player, but he might be the most energetic! An optimistic young boy who's always ready when you are.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 小さな体にエネルギーがいっぱい！ いつも元気な前向き少年。

Name: Gabriel Garcia
Description: A player so stunning in face and figure that some suspect he's a girl. He knows Riccardo well.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 容姿端麗で 女の子だと疑惑を持たれるほど。 神童の良き理解者。

Name: Samguk Han
Description: A persistent player who gets back up however many times he's knocked down. He's a caring guy who looks out for younger players.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 何度倒れても諦めない不屈の姿に 皆が心を打たれる。面倒見がいい人情派。

Name: Subaru Honda
Description: A hot-headed go-getter. Dribbles the ball like a runaway train.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 燃えたぎる 熱いハートを持つ選手。 爆走する機関車のようなドリブルをする。

Name: Wanli Changcheng
Description: The biggest member of the team and a stalwart defender. Hates unfair play.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 大きな体を活かしたディフェンスが得意。 曲がったことが嫌いでケンカっ早い。

Name: Adé Kébé
Description: A canny lad who brightens the team's mood. Sea fishing is his hobby.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: いつも明るく大らかなムードメーカー。 ヒマさえあれば 釣りへ出かけている。

Name: Eugene Peabody
Description: Raimon's fastest midfielder. Has distinctly pessimistic tendencies.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 雷門中イチの 俊足ミッドフィールダー。 ネガティブ思考で すぐスランプになる。

Name: Michael Ballzack
Description: His seemingly unconcerned attitude hides an intense passion for football.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 一見冷めているが その心は サッカーへのやり場のない思いでいっぱい。

Name: Doug McArthur
Description: A proud striker. His skills are the real deal, but he seems a little detached.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: プライド高きストライカー。 能力はあるが どこか冷めている。

Name: Aitor Cazador
Description: A young boy with superb body balance. He has his highs and lows, but is a good kid at heart.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 優れたボディバランスを備えている少年。 二面性があるが根は悪くない。

Name: Ryoma Nishiki
Description: A chivalrous boy with a strong moral compass. Spent some time in Italy.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: イタリア帰りのスーパープレイヤー。 人情を重んじる男気のある性格。

Name: Lucian Dark
Description: An earnest and positive boy. Though a beginner, he has great natural skill.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: ひたむきで明るい少年。初心者離れした サッカーセンスを垣間見せる。

Name: Lars Dijkstra
Description: A cool-headed player who only plays football for the sake of his grades.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: サッカーは内申書のためにやっているという 冷めたプレイヤー。

Name: Sven Johansson
Description: A sly boy. Likes football, but doesn't like to oppose people with power.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: サッカーは好きだが ずる賢く 強い者には逆らわないタイプ。

Name: Mark Evans
Description: The former captain of Inazuma National, turned manager. A passionate leader.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
Team2JP: イナズマレジェンドジャパン
DescriptionJP: 雷門サッカー部監督で元イナズマジャパンの キャプテン。熱血采配でチームを勝利に導く。

Name: Celia Hills
Description: She serves as the advisor for the Raimon football team, always keeping a gentle, watchful eye on the players.
DescriptionJP: 雷門サッカー部の顧問を務める教師。 いつも 部員たちを優しく見守っている。

Name: Skie Blue
Description: A cheerful girl and long-time friend of Arion's. Hard-working team coordinator.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: いつも元気で明るい 天馬の幼なじみ。 マネージャーの中でも 一番のしっかり者。

Name: Rosie Redd
Description: Though a coordinator, spends her time trailing Riccardo with a camera.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 雷門中のマネージャーで 神童の大ファン。 カメラを構えてシャッターチャンスを狙う。

Name: Jade Greene
Description: A rough-and-ready girl who hates injustice. Has taken a liking to Arion.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 雷門の番長で 曲がった事が大嫌い。 天馬をとても気に入っている。

Name: Montaña Tábano
Description: When he visits a buffet, he won't leave until he's absolutely stuffed himself.
DescriptionJP: 恐ろしいほどに 食い意地が張っていて 食べ放題に行くたびに お腹を壊している。

Name: Tom Gato
Description: Always acts frank and blunt, but has a secret habit of caring for stray cats.
DescriptionJP: 言動が淡白で 素っ気ない態度だが 野良ネコによく懐かれる 意外な一面も。

Name: Joaquín Coronado
Description: Hates to lose. Has a tendency to value personal pride over good teamwork.
DescriptionJP: 負けず嫌いで 個人勝負にこだわりがち。 そのため 連携をおろそかにすることも。

Name: Conant Ó Briain
Description: A laid-back lad who refuses to be rushed, no matter the situation.
DescriptionJP: 周囲に惑わされないマイペースさゆえに 好調・不調の波が小さいところが強み。

Name: Sirius Starsky
Description: He considers the star-shaped sticker on his hair a personal trademark.
DescriptionJP: 頭に貼りつけてある星形のシールは 自分の名前になぞらえたトレードマーク。

Name: Shunsuke Aoyama
Description: An analytical player more interested in strategy than physical prowess.
Team2JP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 体力よりも情報で戦いに挑むタイプ。 控えにいる時も 自己分析を欠かさない。

Name: Bucky Woodchuck
Description: A little timid in nature, but very nimble and dexterous with a ball.
DescriptionJP: 臆病な性格で 大胆さに欠けるが 持ち前の器用さを武器にした戦法が得意。

Name: Punkie Mahican
Description: Loves his pet chicken so much he styled his hair into a mohawk like its comb.
DescriptionJP: 家で飼っているニワトリを溺愛するあまり 髪型をトサカ風モヒカンにしてしまった。

Name: Hugues Baudet
Description: Known for helping out his teammates and has a keen sense of strategy.
Team2JP: 雷門ファーストチーム
DescriptionJP: 仲間のフォローやアシストに定評がある。 戦略面で チームを支えることが多い。

Name: Jagur Meister
Description: Doesn't care much for the finer details. Has a bold and powerful style of play.
DescriptionJP: あまり細かいことは考えないタイプ。 言動もプレイも豪快でパワフル。

Name: Friedrich Schiller
Description: An aggressive and instinctive player. Does "Schiller" remind you of anyone?
DescriptionJP: 思わせぶりな言動が多いとよく言われる。 吉良… この名前が意味するものとは…？

Name: Adarn Shame
Description: Isn't very interested in football itself, but plays it for the sake of his grades.
DescriptionJP: サッカー自体に それほど関心はないが 内申書目当てでサッカーを始めた。

Name: Ota Shape
Description: A rather self-centred type who is quick to push for his own opinions.
DescriptionJP: 自分の主張を強引に押し通そうとする 何ともワガママな考えの持ち主。

Name: Nogo Sarikid
Description: Neither top of the class nor a star athlete, but he gets by with clever tricks.
DescriptionJP: 勉強もスポーツもズバ抜けてはいないが 小手先のテクニックで それなりにこなす。

Name: Lance Speares
Description: A steadfast goalkeeper who can read the course of a shot in an instant.
DescriptionJP: 瞬時の判断で シュートコースを正確に読む 強力なゴールキーパー。

Name: Dirk Anlace
Description: Closes in on opposing players at high speed to nip their offensive in the bud.
DescriptionJP: 高速の寄せでスペースをカバーし 相手の攻撃を未然に防ぐ。

Name: Clay Moor
Description: A brawny player who can deflect even the most powerful shot with ease.
DescriptionJP: 鍛え抜いた肉体で どんなシュートも 涼しい顔で弾き返す屈強なプレイヤー。

Name: Nun Chuck
Description: What you see is what you get: a real power fighter. Has a cruel edge to him.
DescriptionJP: 見た目通りのパワーファイター。 相手の苦しむ姿を見て楽しむ残忍な選手。

Name: Spike Stiletto
Description: A rough defender who doesn't hesitate to resort to dirty tactics.
DescriptionJP: ダーティーなプレイも容赦なく仕掛ける 荒ぶるディフェンダー。

Name: Bilbo Baton
Description: Values efficiency above all else, and pursues it in every aspect of his game.
DescriptionJP: 能率至上主義のプレイヤー。 あらゆる動作に効率性を求める。

Name: Jack Knife
Description: Likes to discover his opponents' weak points and take advantage of them.
DescriptionJP: 相手のウィークポイントを見つけて 容赦なく攻め立てる。

Name: Bayonet Gunne
Description: Though his body is small, his kicking strength is borderline destructive.
DescriptionJP: 小柄な体から想像もつかないほどに 破壊的なキック力を持つ。

Name: Howie Itzer
Description: His eyes are two different colors. Has a tendency to be overconfident.
DescriptionJP: 左右で色が違う瞳がトレードマーク。 自身の実力を過信するきらいがある。

Name: Flam Berger
Description: A cool and collected goal hunter. Uninterested in anything but scoring.
DescriptionJP: 冷徹で無機質なゴールハンター。 点を取る事以外には関心が無い。

Name: Matt Chetty
Description: His personality is tricky to read, but his skills speak for themselves.
DescriptionJP: つかみどころのない性格だが サッカーの実力はかなりのもの。

Name: Harold Shields
Description: He may look small and unimposing, but his play is wild and dangerous.
DescriptionJP: カワイイ外見とは裏腹に プレイはとても荒々しくてデンジャラス。

Name: Hal Byrd
Description: All he ever thinks about is how best to achieve his missions from Fifth Sector.
DescriptionJP: 常にフィフスセクターの任務を 忠実に遂行する事だけを考えている。

Name: Morgan Stern
Description: Believes that victory should be earned by crushing the foe without restraint.
DescriptionJP: 相手を負かすなら徹底的にやるべきだ という無慈悲な考えを持つ。

Name: Roman Ballista
Description: Uses remarkable agility to always reach the best position on the pitch.
DescriptionJP: 並外れた瞬発力と跳躍力で フィールドを縦横無尽に駆け回る。

Name: Saber Sabel
Description: The manager of the Black Templars, and a ruthless servant of Fifth Sector.
DescriptionJP: 黒の騎士団の監督。 フィフスセクターの忠実な臣下で冷酷な人物。

Name: Par Scal
Description: Fixed his eyesight with surgery, but still wears glasses as a fashion item.
DescriptionJP: 矯正手術により 視力が良くなったので メガネはアクセサリー感覚で使っている。

Name: Tez La
Description: Can locate his foes through intuition alone. Also a skilled student of Iaido.
DescriptionJP: 勘が鋭く 気配で相手の位置を読む。 居合道の達人で 休日は稽古に励んでいる。

Name: Aris Tottle
Description: Manages the school library, and always knows which books are where.
DescriptionJP: 栄都学園の図書委員長を務めており 蔵書の貸し出しを すべて把握している。

Name: Archie Medes
Description: A talented up-and-coming novelist with five critically acclaimed works published.
DescriptionJP: 知る人ぞ知る 新進気鋭の小説家。 既に５作の小説を発表し 好評を得ている。

Name: Socrat Eiss
Description: Son of the president of a major book store chain. His house is full of books.
DescriptionJP: 父親が 大手ブックストアの社長なので 自宅には あらゆる本が山のようにある。

Name: Ian Stein
Description: A master of shorthand, but so shy that he prefers to write instead of talking.
DescriptionJP: 目にも留まらぬスピードで文字を書く。 シャイな性格で 日常会話も筆談が基本。

Name: Ed Ison
Description: Attends art classes after school. His creative work draws a lot of attention.
DescriptionJP: 駅前のアートスクールに通っている。 独創的な絵を描くので いつも注目の的。

Name: Mitchell Angelio
Description: Reads 10,000 words a minute and is training to go even faster.
DescriptionJP: 速読が得意で １分間に２万文字を読む。 更なるスピードアップを目指して訓練中。

Name: Moe Sart
Description: Comes from a poor family, but attained academic greatness on talent alone.
DescriptionJP: 家が貧しいため 塾も参考書も頼らず 独力で栄都学園のトップ成績を取った。

Name: Dave Inchy
Description: Can study the whole pitch in a second with his remarkable perceptive ability.
DescriptionJP: フィールドの状況を即座に把握できる 優れた洞察力を持った頭脳派キャプテン。

Name: Frank Lyn
Description: Studying hard to become like his dad and grandad, both esteemed scholars.
DescriptionJP: 父も 祖父も 名を馳せた学者なので 自身もそれを目指して 必死に勉強中。

Name: Cooper Nikos
Description: Adores traditional Japanese music and has visited nearly every shrine in Kanto.
DescriptionJP: 雅楽が好きで 神社巡りをしている。 関東地方の神社は あらかた制覇した。

Name: Leo Gally
Description: A narcissistic boy whose dream is to have his portrait on a banknote.
DescriptionJP: 自分の顔が紙幣に使われることを夢見て 自画像を描き続けているナルシスト。

Name: Desmond Cartes
Description: His family is wealthy, but he keeps this a secret to avoid special treatment.
DescriptionJP: 実は 超有名な資産家の御曹司なのだが 特別扱いを嫌って素性を隠している。

Name: Connor Fuschius
Description: A ghostwriter for a literary magazine. It seems he's written a lot of articles.
DescriptionJP: 文芸雑誌のゴーストライターを務め かなりの量の記事を書いているらしい。

Name: Dar Wynne
Description: Girls are his weakness; he can never turn down a request from a pretty face.
DescriptionJP: 女の子に甘く 頼みごとをされると ついつい安請け合いをしてしまう性格。

Name: Tom Jefferson
Description: Prodigy Grammar's manager. Records his players' performances and grades them.
DescriptionJP: 栄都学園サッカー部監督。 選手のプレイを常に記録し 点数をつける。

Name: Starbuck Rogers
Description: A wild goalie who's no stranger to rough play. Oddly quiet in the morning due to low blood pressure.
DescriptionJP: 血気盛んで気性が激しい荒くれキーパー。 低血圧のせいか 朝はテンションが低い。

Name: Worff Chewback
Description: His family runs a café. He created a dish himself, but it wasn't too popular.
DescriptionJP: 両親が自宅で小さな定食屋を営んでいる。 自身も料理を開発したが 評判はイマイチ。

Name: Dart H. Cylon
Description: Though he plays cleanly on the pitch, he's rather unethical elsewhere.
DescriptionJP: 温厚な性格で ラフプレイは好まないが 勝負事に関しては 非道な一面を持つ。

Name: Scotty O'Brien
Description: Has a habit of knocking other players over with his rough shoulder charge.
DescriptionJP: 強烈なタックルが得意なディフェンダー。 相手を転ばせることに快感を覚える。

Name: Billy-Lee Adarma
Description: This fortunate player is always lucky in games of chance, such as tombolas.
DescriptionJP: くじ運が強く 宝くじに当選するのが趣味。 おみくじも 大吉以外は引いたことがない。

Name: Zaphod Riker
Description: The other students call him "Lord Snotty." He's an insufferable snob.
DescriptionJP: 校内では 『プリンス』と持てはやされ 常に 相手を見下した態度を取っている。

Name: Cyber Dalekman
Description: The team's "phantom member," he only ever shows up for actual matches.
DescriptionJP: 試合以外では滅多に姿を見せないので メンバーから 幽霊部員と呼ばれている。

Name: Lucas Skywalk
Description: Used to play football properly, but has come to rely on dirty tricks.
DescriptionJP: かつては真剣にサッカーをしていたが 今では荒んだプレイに終始している。

Name: Jimmy Kyrk
Description: Always very polite, but never stands up to authority and can be heartless.
Team2JP: レジスタンスジャパン
DescriptionJP: 礼儀正しい性格だが 大きな力には逆らえず 非情な面を見せることも。

Name: Harkness Torchwood
Description: His piercing gaze can make out details even in the blackest darkness.
DescriptionJP: 鋭く細い目は 夜行性動物のように 暗闇でも 先を見通すことができるらしい。

Name: Jean-Luc Janeway
Description: His dream is to go to the moon, and he sees football as training for this.
DescriptionJP: 宇宙飛行士になって月面へ行くのが夢。 サッカーは そのための鍛錬という考え。

Name: Wesley Sheridan
Description: Loves anything that comes in threes, from dimensions to little pigs.
DescriptionJP: とにかく三大ナントカの話題が好き。 御三家や三国志など 何でも食いつく。

Name: Sithri Peon
Description: Usually a slacker, but in a crisis he can steal the ball in the blink of an eye.
DescriptionJP: 普段は無気力で やる気のない雰囲気だが いざとなると 優れた瞬発力を発揮する。

Name: Isaac Binks
Description: His dream is to become an expert at crafting bows for archery.
DescriptionJP: 弓道やアーチェリーで使う弓が大好き。 将来は 弓を作る職人になりたいと言う。

Name: Carl Rissian
Description: Feels quite overwhelmed by bright lights, and likes to stay in the shade.
DescriptionJP: 普通の人より 光を眩しく感じる体質で いつも 日陰や暗がりに身をひそめる。

Name: Robert Affett
Description: Particularly proud of his pearly whites, but his glare tends to scare people.
DescriptionJP: 自慢の白い歯をスマイルで見せつけるが 目つきが悪いので 怖がられてしまう。

Name: Deanna Tam
Description: The manager of Milky Way. Don't let her sweet looks deceive you—she is definitely in charge.
DescriptionJP: 天河原中サッカー部監督。 かわいい見ためと裏腹に その采配は過激。

Name: Aum Nirvana
Description: Uses his keen reflexes to grab hold of any shot, regardless of its momentum.
DescriptionJP: ズバ抜けた瞬発力と反射神経の持ち主。 機械いじりが趣味で 自室は工具だらけ。

Name: Adamant Walhalla
Description: Uses his imposing form to pressure opponents. Trains with weights two hours a day.
DescriptionJP: 体格を活かした 強烈なプレスが持ち味。 毎日２時間に及ぶ 筋トレのたまものだ。

Name: Omega Elysium
Description: His greatest weapon is his tough-as- iron body, which can deflect any shot.
DescriptionJP: 鉄のように頑強な肉体が武器。 どんなシュートも体を張って跳ね返す。

Name: Fürimmer Jung
Description: Though small in build, his incredible stamina makes him a potent defender.
DescriptionJP: 小兵だが疲れ知らずのスタミナを武器に 粘り強いディフェンスをする。

Name: Zenith Shangrila
Description: Zips swiftly back and forth, taking his opponents unawares to steal the ball.
DescriptionJP: 相手の意表をつくトリッキーなプレイから 『フィールドの詐欺師』と呼ばれている。

Name: Optimum Limbo
Description: Methodical and steady, he's a master of consistency but slow to pivot.
DescriptionJP: コツコツと堅実に積み重ねていく性格で 安定感はあるが 融通が利かない一面も。

Name: Panacea Utopia
Description: His tricky moves confuse the opposing team, throwing them into disarray.
DescriptionJP: 相手チームの戦術を じわじわ崩していく 敵に回すと厄介なタイプのプレイヤー。

Name: Acme Rapture
Description: A martial-arts genius who achieved instructor rank at the age of ten.
DescriptionJP: 弱冠１０歳で 道場の師範代となった天才。 卓越した体術を サッカーに応用して戦う。

Name: Ultima Nextworld
Description: A cool-headed master of analysis. Also plays keyboard in a band.
DescriptionJP: クールな音楽を こよなく愛している。 友達と組んだバンドではキーボード担当。

Name: Maxim Millennium
Description: A tricksy manipulator who uses words and actions to influence his foes.
DescriptionJP: 巧みなボールさばきによるフェイントと 狡猾な言動で 相手を翻弄してもてあそぶ。

Name: Infinity Beyond
Description: A striker with tremendous power. His kicks are like sharpened blades.
DescriptionJP: 勝つために手段を厭わないストライカー。 繰り出すキックは 切れ味鋭い刃のよう。

Name: Apex Paradiso
Description: Always worried about his stiff joints. Stretching doesn't seem to help much.
DescriptionJP: 全身の関節が 異常に硬いのが悩み。 ストレッチをしても改善する気配はない。

Name: Pearl Gates
Description: His whole family is into mixed martial arts. Often spars with his dad for fun.
DescriptionJP: 家族全員が総合格闘技の熱狂的なファン。 父と技を掛け合うのが日課になっている。

Name: Perpetuo Xanadu
Description: Displays incredible concentration skills, but only at critical moments.
DescriptionJP: 本番に強く ここ一番という場面になると 人並み外れた すごい集中力を発揮する。

Name: Sempiterno Bliss
Description: A top sprinter in the track and field club. Football is his secondary hobby.
DescriptionJP: 万能坂中陸上部のトップスプリンター。 サッカー部には掛け持ちで参加している。

Name: Myriad Arcadia
Description: Collects toy banknotes because it makes him feel like a millionaire.
DescriptionJP: お金持ちに強い憧れを抱いており おもちゃのお札を集めて楽しんでいる。

Name: Primo Eden
Description: Almighty Faith's manager. Will stop at nothing to achieve victory.
DescriptionJP: 万能坂中サッカー部監督。 勝つためには手段を選ばない非情さを持つ。

Name: Preston Princeton
Description: Powerful yet graceful saves are his trademark. His success rate is sublime.
DescriptionJP: 激しくも美しいセービングが身上のＧＫ。 帝国学園の連続無失点記録を持つ実力派。

Name: Dracon Yale
Description: A formidable defender, skilled in all areas: power, technique and speed.
DescriptionJP: フィジカル・テクニック・スピード 全てを備えた脅威のディフェンダー。

Name: Duke Dartmouth
Description: Opposing teams have been known to tremble at his brutal defensive skills.
DescriptionJP: 巨体を駆使した 荒々しいディフェンスは 相手を震え上がらせるほどダイナミック。

Name: Cameron Cambridge
Description: A utility player, able to adjust his play style to suit the situation at hand.
DescriptionJP: 戦況に応じ 柔軟にプレイスタイルを変える 帝国学園のユーティリティプレイヤー。

Name: Earl Eton
Description: Like a runaway train on the pitch, he crushes the foe with vicious tackles.
DescriptionJP: 怒りに身を任せたプレイをすることから フィールドの怒れる暴走列車と呼ばれる。

Name: Caesar Cornell
Description: A cold fellow who will never hold back even if his enemy is weak or injured.
DescriptionJP: たとえ 初心者やケガ人が相手であろうと 手加減は一切しない 冷徹な性格。

Name: Hampton Harvard
Description: A quick-witted boy whose airy attitude can always lighten the mood.
DescriptionJP: ひょうひょうとした態度と人当たりで 場を和ませる 帝国のムードメーカー。

Name: Baron Oxford
Description: Holds a near-fanatical belief in his team's superiority on the pitch.
DescriptionJP: 帝国学園が決めた やりかたやルールは すべて正しいと信じて疑わず行動する。

Name: Sterling Stanford
Description: So strict about regulations that his friends call him a "demon sergeant."
DescriptionJP: 規律や風紀に とことん厳しい性格で チームメイトから 鬼軍曹と呼ばれている。

Name: Colby Columbia
Description: His powers of observation never miss a telltale sign or opportunity.
DescriptionJP: 観察眼に優れた 帝国のストライカー。 相手のクセや 一瞬のスキを見逃さない。

Name: Rex Remington
Description: Never loud or violent, but opponents feel intimidated by his fierce gaze.
DescriptionJP: 冷静沈着な物腰だが 鋭い眼光と むき出しの闘志に 相手は圧倒される。

Name: Fred Featherstonhaugh
Description: Much more agile than his huge body would suggest, but often careless.
DescriptionJP: 巨体に似合わない身軽さを武器とするが 軽率なプレイでミスをすることも…。

Name: Arthur Ascot
Description: Has remarkable latent abilities, but his negative attitude holds him back.
DescriptionJP: 高い潜在能力を秘めている選手だが ネガティブ思考が 成長を妨げている。

Name: Stuart St John
Description: Good at surprising the foe with trick shots. Not so good at ordinary play.
DescriptionJP: トリックプレイで意表を突くのが得意。 …が 正々堂々と勝負を挑まれると脆い。

Name: Wenceslas Wales
Description: Favours a solid and reliable style of play, well grounded in theory.
DescriptionJP: 奇をてらおうとせず セオリーを重視した 堅実なプレイが持ち味の 真面目な選手。

Name: Yorick York
Description: Fearless and impulsive. His actions surprise even his own team, at times.
DescriptionJP: 怖いもの知らずで 向こう見ずな性格。 大胆な行動で 周囲を驚かせることも。

Name: Jude Sharp
Game: Inazuma Eleven GO Chrono Stones: Wildfire / Thunderflash
Description: Royal Academy's supreme commander and manager. Still as sharp as ever.
TeamJP: 雷門ファーストチーム
Team2JP: イナズマレジェンドジャパン
DescriptionJP: 帝国学園の総帥にして サッカー部監督。 その天才的な頭脳は 未だ衰えてはいない。

Name: David Samford
Game: Inazuma Eleven GO Chrono Stones: Wildfire / Thunderflash
Description: Royal Academy's ever-loyal assistant coach, always backing up Manager Jude.
Team2JP: イナズマレジェンドジャパン
DescriptionJP: 帝国学園サッカー部のコーチを務める。 監督である鬼道を支えている参謀役だ。

Name: Ishmael Ahab
Description: A master of free-diving, with amazing muscles and lung capacity.
DescriptionJP: 人並み外れた 肺活量と筋力の持ち主。 素潜りの達人として 海王学園では有名。

Name: Octavus Kraken
Description: His trademark is an unusual kick where he snaps his leg forward like a whip.
DescriptionJP: ムチのようにしなる足を振り抜いて放つ 変則フォームによるキックが持ち味。

Name: Roger Jolly
Description: Marks opposing players with dogged persistence. Very difficult to escape.
DescriptionJP: 粘り強く執拗なマークが持ち味。 彼のマークから逃れる事は難しい。

Name: Sinbad Saylor
Description: Fluidly shifts between offensive and defensive play as conditions demand.
DescriptionJP: どのポジションでもソツなくこなし チームのダイナモとして活躍する。

Name: Rob Crusoe
Description: A calm player, with the strength to never lose his cool in any situation.
DescriptionJP: 相手に何を言われようとも動じない 穏やかな性格と強いメンタリティを持つ。

Name: Cheung Po
Description: Power play is his field of expertise. Interestingly, he's also a good cook.
DescriptionJP: 体格を活かしたパワープレイが得意。 料理が得意という 意外な一面も…。

Name: William Kidd
Description: An adventurous schoolboy who has single-handedly crossed the Pacific.
DescriptionJP: 趣味のサバイバルを突き詰めた結果 たった１人で 太平洋の横断を達成した。

Name: Santelmo Phyre
Description: Midfielder who lives for aquatic shoulder wars, Pirates Cove's wildest event.
DescriptionJP: 海王の体育大会で 一番人気の種目である 水上騎馬戦が好きなミッドフィールダー。

Name: Dakkar Nemo
Description: Finds everyday life boring. Collects rumors of supernatural phenomena.
DescriptionJP: 退屈な日常を嫌い いつも刺激を求めて 超常現象や都市伝説を追っているらしい。

Name: Davy Jones
Description: The captain of Pirates Cove, sporting great power, technique and zeal.
Team2JP: レジスタンスジャパン
DescriptionJP: 強気で荒々しい 海王学園のキャプテン。 その振る舞いは 海賊に憧れてのものだ。

Name: Calico Corsair
Description: Able to battle his way through any defence and create chances to score.
DescriptionJP: 相手のディフェンスが どんなに強固でも 果敢に切り込んで チャンスメイクする。

Name: Nick Tofobia
Description: At night, he always sleeps curled up with a blanket over his head.
DescriptionJP: 寝るときはいつも 布団を頭からかぶり まるでカメのように 背中を丸めて眠る。

Name: Marley Hookson
Description: At night, she's alive by the sea, always drawn to the waves' endless rhythm.
DescriptionJP: 夜の暗い海が好きで 日が暮れてから 海岸へ出かけては 時間を忘れて眺める。

Name: Bart Black
Description: His abilities are excellent, but his rebellious attitude can cause trouble.
DescriptionJP: 反抗的な態度で 周囲の人間を困らせる 海王学園サッカー部のトラブルメーカー。

Name: Frank Drake
Description: Opponents feel the pressure just at the sight of him standing on the pitch.
DescriptionJP: ただその場に立っているだけなのに なぜか 相手にプレッシャーを与える。

Name: Barnabas Rossa
Description: Obsessed with seabirds, he spends weekends on the coast with binoculars.
DescriptionJP: ウミツバメの観察が 趣味とのことで 休日には 双眼鏡を片手に海岸へ出かける。

Name: Longjohn Silver
Description: Manager of Pirates Cove. Leads with a stern hand, but aims for glorious victories.
DescriptionJP: 海王学園サッカー部監督。 荒々しい采配で 豪快に勝利をつかみ取る。

Name: Alessandro il Grande
Description: Lunar Sea's strategic leader, who can devise a plan for any situation.
DescriptionJP: 刻一刻と移りゆく戦況を 瞬時に察して 的確な指示を送る 月山国光の司令塔。

Name: Gene Ghiskhan
Description: After club activities, he recovers by eating steamed pork buns bought in bulk.
DescriptionJP: 部活で消耗した体力を 回復するために コンビニで肉まんをまとめ買いして帰る。

Name: Attila Hun
Description: Barrels up the field with low-slung dribbling power. Built like a tank and moves like one too.
DescriptionJP: 低重心のドリブルで 攻め上がっていく その姿は しばしば重戦車に例えられる。

Name: Sun Tzu
Description: Controls the team's defence as a rear commander. Good at covering space.
DescriptionJP: バックラインを統率する 守備の指揮官。 味方選手のカバーに回ることが多い。

Name: Arty Xerxes
Description: Near impossible to read. Always seems to be one step ahead of his opponent.
DescriptionJP: 何を考えているか まるで読めない。 トリッキーな動きで相手の意表を突く。

Name: Darius Cyrus
Description: Stoic, and harsh on both himself and others. Guides the team's movements.
DescriptionJP: 己にも他人にも厳しいストイックな選手。 彼の日常生活は まるで修行僧のようだ。

Name: Jerry Onimo
Description: Wants to become a policeman! A hard- working student who's big on justice.
DescriptionJP: 将来の夢は 街を守る警察官になること。 正義感あふれる とてもマジメな中学生。

Name: Leon Ohnepart
Description: Closes in on the opponent in a flash with movements honed to perfection.
DescriptionJP: 無駄が一切なく 洗練された動きと 身軽なフットワークで 間合いを詰める。

Name: Robert Lee
Description: Heir to an ancient two-sword fighting style. His instincts are top-notch.
DescriptionJP: 二刀剣術『天地双刃流』の継承者で 研ぎ澄まされた 勘の鋭さはピカイチ。

Name: Nobby Naga
Description: Once a benchwarmer, he clawed into the starting lineup through sheer grit and nonstop hustle.
DescriptionJP: 以前は控え選手だったが 努力の結果 レギュラー選手の座を勝ち取ったという。

Name: Salvador Addin
Description: A skilled player, but quite headstrong. Not great at coordinating with others.
DescriptionJP: 月山国光の控えゴールキーパーだが 我が強く 兵頭のような指示は出せない。

Name: Otto Bismark
Description: His grandfather was German. Rather straight-laced and by-the-book.
DescriptionJP: ドイツ人の祖父を持つクォーター。 一言で言えば堅物で とても頑固者。

Name: Jean Darc
Description: Has no flashy moves of his own, but provides valuable support to the team.
DescriptionJP: 注目を浴びるような行動はしないが 縁の下の力持ちという言葉が似合う。

Name: Bobby Bruce
Description: Often claims that his muscles are his life. His hobby is bench pressing.
DescriptionJP: 「筋肉を鍛える事は生きがい！」が口癖。 好きなトレーニングは ベンチプレス。

Name: Hanny Bawl
Description: A military gear junkie who snacks on ration packs like candy.
DescriptionJP: ミリタリーグッズを集めるのが好きで いつも戦闘食のレーションを食べている。

Name: Sturm Schwartzkopf
Description: Lunar Sea's manager, and a tactician in the pay of Fifth Sector.
DescriptionJP: 月山国光中サッカー部監督。 フィフスセクターで一二を争う策士。

Name: Wolfe Whyte
Description: A goalie as impassable as a wall. Believes that winning is everything.
DescriptionJP: 白恋中のキャプテンを務めるキーパー。 勝つことに強いこだわりを持っている。

Name: Sascha Kotch
Description: A living legend who clears whole neighborhoods of snow with just a shovel.
DescriptionJP: スコップ一つで あっという間に 町内の雪を片付けてしまう 雪かきの名人。

Name: Guy l'Acier
Description: Had a life-changing grilled salmon encounter and now studies salmon behavior nonstop.
DescriptionJP: 焼き鮭の味に感銘を受けて以来 ずっと 鮭の生態について 研究をしている。

Name: Matther Horne
Description: Often helps out at the port warehouse, and has the muscles to show for it.
DescriptionJP: 放課後は 筋力トレーニングも兼ねて 近くの港で 船の積み荷を手伝っている。

Name: Iggie Loo
Description: His family farms lilies for a living. Their bulbs always fetch a high price.
DescriptionJP: 地元で有名なユリ農家で 球根はいつもプレミア価格になる。

Name: Bob Sled
Description: Does environmental work, teaching tourists not to feed the local wildlife.
DescriptionJP: 野生動物にエサを与えないよう呼びかけ 観光客のマナーアップを目指している。

Name: Blain Chills
Description: Skilled at ice fishing; he can drill a perfect hole in the ice with his foot.
DescriptionJP: 凍った湖での ワカサギ釣りが趣味。 華麗な足技で 氷に穴を開けるという。

Name: Art Tundra
Description: Has taken over 2,000 photographs of frost-covered trees as a hobby.
DescriptionJP: 雪山を訪れては 樹氷の写真を撮っている。 その数はついに２０００枚を超えたという。

Name: Borel Aurora
Description: Able to swim in freezing winter rivers. Claims it's because of his herring diet.
DescriptionJP: 真冬の川で平然と泳ぐ すごいヤツ。 ニシンとカズノコが 彼の元気の源。

Name: Njord Snio
Description: The hottest striker of the north, scouted out by Shawn Froste.
DescriptionJP: 白恋ＯＢの吹雪に その才能を見出された 北国屈指のスーパーストライカーだ。

Name: Yule Hoarfrost
Description: A speed skater first and foremost. His legs are terrifyingly strong.
DescriptionJP: 本来はスピードスケートの選手。 その足腰の強さはハンパじゃない。

Name: Suno Aisu
Description: Originally from the far east of Japan. His greatest wish is world peace.
DescriptionJP: 日本の最東端からやって来た少年。 心の底から 世界の平和を願っている。

Name: Himesh Himalaya
Description: Studying the local deer population and seeking ways to preserve their habitat.
DescriptionJP: 生態系を守るために できることを考え とりあえず エゾシカの観察を始めた。

Name: Blake Wintry
Description: A skilled tree climber. Nimble enough to leap from one tree to another.
DescriptionJP: 猿に負けずとも劣らない身のこなしで 木から木へと飛び移る 木登りの達人。

Name: Fritz Brisk
Description: An expert mountaineer with a tough body and keen decision-making skills.
DescriptionJP: 超危険な 冬山登山のエキスパート。 タフな体と冷静な判断力を併せ持っている。

Name: Grisley Bear
Description: A dangerous boy who likes to injure others and has the strength to do so.
DescriptionJP: 相手の選手に ケガを負わせることで 喜びを感じるという キケンなぶっ壊し屋。

Name: Wilder Bigfoot
Description: The manager of Alpine Junior High. Favors brute strength over detailed strategy.
DescriptionJP: 白恋中サッカー部監督。 細かい戦略よりも 力押しの采配が得意。

Name: Strom Boojum
Description: Seems like a tough, opinionated guy, but is actually kind of mellow.
DescriptionJP: 非常に気の強そうな顔をしているが 見かけによらず かなり穏やかな性格。

Name: Dock Hickory
Description: Practices his regatta skills rowing down the river. He's pretty macho.
DescriptionJP: ボート競技 レガッタの練習をしている。 そのため 上半身はずいぶんと鍛えられた。

Name: Bourne Birch
Description: The descendant of a local hero. Doesn't talk about it, though.
DescriptionJP: ある偉人の末裔だというが 本人はその事について語ろうとはしない。

Name: Flynt Pine
Description: Likes to dart around here and there, leaving his opponent in disarray.
DescriptionJP: フィールドを ちょこまかと動きまわり 相手をかく乱するようなスタイルが得意。

Name: Trent Poplar
Description: Enjoys going jogging around the local lakes and ponds.
DescriptionJP: 公園にある大きな湖や 池の周囲を ぐるりと回ってランニングするのが好き。

Name: River Willows
Description: At night he plays guitar and sings as a street musician.
DescriptionJP: 放課後はストリートミュージシャンとして 駅前などで ギターの弾き語りをしている。

Name: Beck Heath
Description: His family has an esteemed history in traditional theatre.
DescriptionJP: 能楽界のお坊ちゃんで サッカーは あくまで たしなみの一つに過ぎない。

Name: Brook Linden
Description: Has a short fuse—he's liable to get heated up about the smallest things.
DescriptionJP: 短気な性格で 些細な事でもすぐに ヒートアップしてしまうクセがある。

Name: Bay Laurel
Description: A star player with real pro potential. Spends every waking moment training.
DescriptionJP: プロも注目しているスタープレイヤー。 練習の虫で 常に努力を怠らない。

Name: Langford Ash
Description: Bradford's older brother. Confident, but can get rather arrogant at times.
DescriptionJP: 快彦の兄。自信家のため他を見下し スタンドプレイを取ることも。

Name: Escott Aspen
